# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3
translate spanish d21a_54b81f2e:

    # "Some time has passed since I last visited [I]. I wonder if her friend, Sonmi was her name, has returned to her..."
    "Ha pasado algo de tiempo desde la última vez que visité a [I]. Me pregunto si su amiga, Sonmi se llamaba, habrá vuelto con ella..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:16
translate spanish d21a_2ebc93b9:

    # Z "[I]? It's me.{w=2}{nw}"
    Z "¿[I]? Soy yo.{w=2}{nw}"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:19
translate spanish d21a_41a9bb42:

    # I "...{w=3}{nw}"
    I "… {w=3}{nw}"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:22
translate spanish d21a_51ecdc6f:

    # I "It's good to see you again, [persistent.player_name]."
    I "Me alegro de verte de nuevo, [persistent.player_name]."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:25
translate spanish d21a_ac46fede:

    # Z "Are you alone or did your friend return?"
    Z "¿Estás sola o ha vuelto tu amiga?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:28
translate spanish d21a_41688ea0:

    # I "...she did. She is inside."
    I "… sí, ha vuelto. Está dentro."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:31
translate spanish d21a_a662881b:

    # Z "Good. Because it's best for you both to be there, for this."
    Z "Bien. Porque es mejor que estéis las dos para esto."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:34
translate spanish d21a_0cf06034:

    # I "...?"
    I "¿...?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:35
translate spanish d21a_62a3473d:

    # Z "I promised to take you back to your old home. The day has come."
    Z "Te prometí que te llevaría de vuelta a tu antiguo hogar. Ha llegado el día."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:38
translate spanish d21a_f4eb62b2:

    # Z "But before that, I think I need to know more of what happened back there. To understand more."
    Z "Pero antes de eso, creo que necesito saber más de lo que pasó allí. Para entenderlo mejor."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:41
translate spanish d21a_5018f220:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:44
translate spanish d21a_dc47a6e3:

    # I "I see."
    I "Ya veo."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:50
translate spanish d21a_6cd57366:

    # "As you move towards the entrance..."
    "Mientras te diriges hacia la entrada..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:53
translate spanish d21a_357de69c:

    # I "[persistent.player_name]! Wait..."
    I "¡[persistent.player_name]! Espera..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:56
translate spanish d21a_a6596a1e:

    # I "Please, do not..."
    I "Por favor, no..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:59
translate spanish d21a_ae6b111f:

    # I "Do not call for her yet. She is resting."
    I "No la llames todavía. Está descansando."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:62
translate spanish d21a_b5b3edc0:

    # Z "Understood."
    Z "Entendido."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:72
translate spanish d21a_56a28647:

    # Yu "The second and fourth files are the ones you want to read."
    Yu "El segundo y el cuarto archivo son los que quieres leer."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:75
translate spanish d21a_fb2280d1:

    # Z "If I remember right, those were locked last time, weren't they?"
    Z "Si mal no recuerdo, esos estaban bloqueados la última vez, ¿no?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:88
translate spanish d21a_946885c3:

    # Z "\"High-rise\", \"What I saw\"..."
    Z "\"El Rascacielos\", \"Lo que vi\"..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:89
translate spanish d21a_05460f0c:

    # Yu "The first one was from long before the... attack."
    Yu "El primero era de mucho antes del... ataque."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:99
translate spanish d21a12_46f896e3:

    # "More than eighty years earlier..."
    "Más de ochenta años antes..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:100
translate spanish d21a12_c931a3ed:

    # So "Come on, Yuna! You sound like Aloi!"
    So "¡Venga, Yuna! ¡Pareces Aloi!"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:101
translate spanish d21a12_3e28c1ca:

    # Yu "Are you sure this is a good idea?"
    Yu "¿Seguro que es una buena idea?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:104
translate spanish d21a12_ac0bedc8:

    # So "It doesn't hurt to try!"
    So "¡Intentarlo no duele!"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:105
translate spanish d21a12_68715a94:

    # So "I mean... Wherever these people come from, they must be desperate to explore this place."
    So "Quiero decir... Vengan de donde vengan, deben estar desesperados por explorar este lugar."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:106
translate spanish d21a12_e5332d04:

    # Yu "I... agree with others... we shouldn't trust them."
    Yu "Yo... coincido con los demás... no deberíamos confiar en ellos."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:107
translate spanish d21a12_de415f2a:

    # So "But what if that's why they ended up in this place? Because people outside didn't trust them, just like they don't trust our kind?"
    So "¿Pero y si por eso acabaron en este sitio? ¿Porque la gente de fuera no confiaba en ellos, igual que no confían en los de nuestra clase?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:110
translate spanish d21a12_ac020f35:

    # So "Did you know they actually entered the inner parts of the city?"
    So "¿Sabías que llegaron a entrar en las partes interiores de la ciudad?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:111
translate spanish d21a12_dd3aca2c:

    # So "That's what they told me, at least. It would explain why their appearance changed so much, eventually."
    So "Eso es lo que me contaron ellos, al menos. Eso explicaría por qué su aspecto cambió tanto, con el tiempo."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:114
translate spanish d21a12_1964f29e:

    # Yu "You... talked to them? Where?"
    Yu "¿Tú... hablaste con ellos? ¿Dónde?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:117
translate spanish d21a12_4d2c381b:

    # So "J-just... somewhere outside, of course."
    So "S-solo... en algún sitio fuera, claro."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:120
translate spanish d21a12_d066e2f9:

    # So "Don't worry, I didn't give away where we live, or anything specific!"
    So "No te preocupes, no dije dónde vivimos, ¡ni nada concreto!"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:123
translate spanish d21a12_28756b31:

    # Yu "Sonmi, we talked about this..."
    Yu "Sonmi, hablamos de esto..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:127
translate spanish d21a12_342d62f7:

    # So "Yuna, I know you have seen more of this world than me. But I also want to learn more, you know?"
    So "Yuna, sé que has visto más de este mundo que yo. Pero yo también quiero aprender más, ¿sabes?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:128
translate spanish d21a12_1f355ee7:

    # I "I understand, but..."
    I "Lo entiendo, pero..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:129
translate spanish d21a12_1dcfd477:

    # So "But it's not just about that!"
    So "¡Pero no es solo por eso!"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:133
translate spanish d21a12_0f3bd1d4:

    # Yu "Where are you going? Be careful!"
    Yu "¿Dónde vas? ¡Ten cuidado!"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:134
translate spanish d21a12_a85ae955:

    # So "Isn't it obvious? No one who comes into the city truly stays here willingly. Neither do we, really!"
    So "¿No es obvio? Nadie que viene a la ciudad se queda aquí de verdad por voluntad propia. ¡Nosotros tampoco, la verdad!"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:135
translate spanish d21a12_91eb6772:

    # So "Sure, we have the tower, but if we didn't have to hide from those desert people, perhaps we would have found another safe place by now..."
    So "Claro, tenemos la torre, pero si no tuviéramos que escondernos de esa gente del desierto, quizá ya habríamos encontrado otro lugar seguro..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:136
translate spanish d21a12_b18feb1c:

    # So "A place with clean air, maybe!"
    So "¡Un lugar con aire limpio, quizá!"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:139
translate spanish d21a12_c2b8cdd2:

    # So "Anyway, we're here now and it is what it is... we should stick together. What do you think?"
    So "Bueno, ya estamos aquí y es lo que hay... deberíamos permanecer unidas. ¿Qué opinas?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:142
translate spanish d21a12_5e99edfa:

    # Yu "As you say, I have been to other places before. There are many people who are desperate and it often means they don't necessarily want what's good for you."
    Yu "Como dices, he estado en otros sitios antes. Hay mucha gente desesperada y eso suele significar que no necesariamente quieren lo que es bueno para ti."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:143
translate spanish d21a12_d9e24a4a:

    # Yu "Many times, it's the exact opposite."
    Yu "Muchas veces, es todo lo contrario."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:146
translate spanish d21a12_fedd96e1:

    # So "I know that. All I'm saying is, we can't paint everybody with the same brush! Not everybody is that way."
    So "Lo sé. Lo que digo es que no podemos meter a todos en el mismo saco. No todo el mundo es así."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:147
translate spanish d21a12_f7422a56:

    # So "Maybe that's exactly the mistake people made back then, why all of this happened in the first place."
    So "Quizá ese fue exactamente el error que cometió la gente entonces, la razón de que todo esto ocurriera en primer lugar."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:150
translate spanish d21a12_fe2309e0:

    # So "They saw this city and thought it wasn't worth saving, so they left it to rot. They only saw the mud, and not the diamonds hidden underneath."
    So "Vieron esta ciudad y pensaron que no merecía la pena salvarla, así que la dejaron pudrirse. Solo vieron el barro, y no los diamantes escondidos debajo."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:151
translate spanish d21a12_fc377fe1:

    # Yu "Sonmi, you're going too far..."
    Yu "Sonmi, te estás pasando..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:154
translate spanish d21a12_3d0514d9:

    # So "Come on, Yuna! You've read the same books I am reading. \"Do whatever you can't not do\"!"
    So "¡Vamos, Yuna! Has leído los mismos libros que yo. \"Haz aquello que no puedas dejar de hacer\"."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:157
translate spanish d21a12_faa204aa:

    # Yu "Alright, that's enough! What you're doing is dangerous!"
    Yu "¡Basta ya! ¡Lo que estás haciendo es peligroso!"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:160
translate spanish d21a12_b51f21c1:

    # Yu "Come back, please..."
    Yu "Vuelve, por favor..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:163
translate spanish d21a12_82d14c97:

    # So "Woow... you should see this!"
    So "¡Guau... deberías ver esto!"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:164
translate spanish d21a12_fa309743:

    # So "Have you ever seen the city laid out under your feet from this high? It's beautiful."
    So "¿Has visto alguna vez la ciudad extendida bajo tus pies desde tan alto? Es precioso."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:167
translate spanish d21a12_074fd5d1:

    # So "I can't imagine what it must have looked like befor-"
    So "No me imagino cómo debió de ser an-"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:171
translate spanish d21a12_a685b09c:

    # So "Ah-!"
    So "¡Ah-!"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:174
translate spanish d21a12_e8dd5b63:

    # I "Sonmi!"
    I "¡Sonmi!"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:181
translate spanish d21a12_1d65b141:

    # Yu "..."
    Yu "..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:184
translate spanish d21a12_19cac674:

    # Yu "The next part... is Sonmi's writings."
    Yu "La siguiente parte... son los escritos de Sonmi."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:187
translate spanish d21a12_00ec21cd:

    # Z "So this is what happened? But why did she..."
    Z "¿Así que esto fue lo que pasó? Pero, ¿por qué ella..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:190
translate spanish d21a12_5994c1c6:

    # I "We thought that writing the words could help her make peace with it."
    I "Pensamos que escribir aquello podría ayudarla a hacer las paces con ello."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:195
translate spanish d21a12_c9063700:

    # "As you read through her detailed accounts of the incident, your burning questions begin to find some answers..."
    "Mientras lees sus detallados relatos del incidente, tus preguntas más acuciantes empiezan a encontrar respuesta..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:196
translate spanish d21a12_06bbc605:

    # "She was there for all of it. Not from a distance. Not in fragments passed down through someone else's retelling."
    "Ella estuvo allí para todo. No a distancia. No en fragmentos transmitidos a través del relato de otra persona."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:197
translate spanish d21a12_a84970f4:

    # "She witnessed every moment firsthand, the kind of thing that doesn't just stay in your memories, but settles into your soul, your dreams, and refuses to leave."
    "Fue testigo de cada momento en primera persona, del tipo de cosas que no se quedan solo en los recuerdos, sino que se instalan en tu alma, en tus sueños, y se niegan a irse."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:198
translate spanish d21a12_45a5cad7:

    # "Whoever she was before that day, some part of her died that day."
    "Fuera quien fuese antes de ese día, una parte de ella murió aquel día."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:199
translate spanish d21a12_2c4d77a2:

    # "Something in her had shifted permanently, irrevocably, and you can feel it in every word she wrote. It reads like an gaping wound."
    "Algo en ella cambió para siempre, de forma irrevocable, y puedes sentirlo en cada palabra que escribió. Se lee como una herida abierta."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:201
translate spanish d21a12_18cbc896:

    # Z "I see it now."
    Z "Ahora lo veo."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:204
translate spanish d21a12_b78fc030:

    # I "The things your people call the decayed... they are still there."
    I "Las cosas que tu gente llama los Decaídos... siguen allí."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:205
translate spanish d21a12_35925e02:

    # I "Perhaps, likely, not the same ones, and maybe not inside the tower, but they still linger in the same place. This is where I was caught."
    I "Quizá, probablemente, no sean los mismos, y tal vez no dentro de la torre, pero siguen merodeando por el mismo lugar. Aquí fue donde me atraparon."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:208
translate spanish d21a12_c5fdd87e:

    # Z "I have dealt with them before, for many years. What happened to you, will not happen again."
    Z "Me he enfrentado a ellos antes, durante muchos años. Lo que te pasó a ti, no volverá a ocurrir."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:211
translate spanish d21a12_5b4a994a:

    # Z "I will make sure of it."
    Z "Me aseguraré de ello."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:212
translate spanish d21a12_1298f1f8:

    # Z "Is there anything else that keeps you from entering the tower?"
    Z "¿Hay algo más que te impida entrar en la torre?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:215
translate spanish d21a12_1f0e1d72:

    # I "No... the bunker is accessed through the same code as the one in the desert."
    I "No... el búnker se abre con el mismo código que el del desierto."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:216
translate spanish d21a12_f631739b:

    # Z "Good. Then we need to let your friend know that..."
    Z "Bien. Entonces tenemos que decirle a tu amiga que..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:218
translate spanish d21a12_f60fc287:

    # I "She's already here."
    I "Ya está aquí."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:221
translate spanish d21a12_9e1f1705:

    # So "What have I missed?!"
    So "¡¿Qué me he perdido?!"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:222
translate spanish d21a12_5018f220:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:225
translate spanish d21a12_88471822:

    # So "Don't tell me you still want to go out there again..."
    So "No me digas que todavía quieres volver a salir allí..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:228
translate spanish d21a12_efa2fecb:

    # Z "{i}*sigh*{/i}"
    Z "{i}*suspiro*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:231
translate spanish d21a12_57ed44dc:

    # "You stand up..."
    "Te pones de pie..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:234
translate spanish d21a12_09e28984:

    # Z "If you're unwilling to listen to your friend, listen to me instead."
    Z "Si no quieres escuchar a tu amiga, escúchame a mí."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:235
translate spanish d21a12_2e921208:

    # Z "I have read everything. I know what you both witnessed."
    Z "Lo he leído todo. Sé lo que presenciasteis las dos."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:238
translate spanish d21a12_aef971d6:

    # Z "You have been carrying this for longer than I have been alive, and it still hurts you to this day. This much is clear to me."
    Z "Has cargado con esto durante más tiempo del que llevo yo vivo, y aún te duele hasta hoy. Eso lo tengo claro."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:239
translate spanish d21a12_eb43e9a7:

    # Z "...The same is true for her."
    Z "...Lo mismo es cierto para ella."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:242
translate spanish d21a12_5018f220_1:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:245
translate spanish d21a12_9ef1242c:

    # Z "But she has dealt with that pain."
    Z "Pero ella ha sabido lidiar con ese dolor."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:248
translate spanish d21a12_22c7a9b2:

    # Z "She even tried to go back to that place for you, and ended up getting caught for her troubles.."
    Z "Incluso intentó volver a ese lugar por ti, y acabó siendo capturada por su esfuerzo..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:249
translate spanish d21a12_8efbcb7f:

    # Z "Had I not encountered her by chance, she would have died."
    Z "Si no me la hubiera encontrado por casualidad, habría muerto."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:252
translate spanish d21a12_51607195:

    # So "..."
    So "..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:253
translate spanish d21a12_0b42e04e:

    # Z "If you honour the risks she was willing to take for you, the least you can do is listen to her, after all these years."
    Z "Si valoras los riesgos que estuvo dispuesta a correr por ti, lo mínimo que puedes hacer es escucharla, después de todos estos años."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:256
translate spanish d21a12_a45b34df:

    # Z "Anyway, I've decided to escort you two back to the old tower. This is her wish for you."
    Z "En fin, he decidido escoltaros a las dos de vuelta a la vieja torre. Ese es su deseo para ti."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:259
translate spanish d21a12_b440ac9b:

    # "You approach [I]..."
    "Te acercas a [I]..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:262
translate spanish d21a12_824241e5:

    # Z "I have been to the inner city before. It's actually pretty readily accessible from this place."
    Z "He estado en la ciudad interior antes. En realidad es bastante accesible desde aquí."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:265
translate spanish d21a12_54e245d3:

    # Z "So what do you say..."
    Z "Así que, ¿qué dices..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:269
translate spanish d21a12_4b8cd47b:

    # Z "Do you want to go for a ride?"
    Z "¿Quieres dar un paseo?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:272
translate spanish d21a12_5018f220_2:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:283
translate spanish d21a12_5018f220_3:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:286
translate spanish d21a12_e8cecd43:

    # Z "This should be the place, right?"
    Z "Este debería ser el sitio, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:287
translate spanish d21a12_de40aa9b:

    # I "...yes."
    I "...sí."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:290
translate spanish d21a12_76da2bb7:

    # Z "Let's stick together, then. I see those living corpses wandering around everywhere."
    Z "Entonces, mantengámonos juntos. Veo esos cadáveres vivientes merodeando por todas partes."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:293
translate spanish d21a12_5054c7d6:

    # Z "You brought your bow, [I]."
    Z "Has traído tu arco, [I]."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:294
translate spanish d21a12_cf582c67:

    # Z "Be ready to use it."
    Z "Prepárate para usarlo."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:297
translate spanish d21a12_d124b278:

    # "You take a long look at the scene stretching before you. The blood-soaked light paints the ruins of this city quarter with a red hue."
    "Observas detenidamente la escena que se extiende ante ti. La luz ensangrentada tiñe las ruinas de este barrio de la ciudad con un tono rojizo."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:298
translate spanish d21a12_8a45f4ec:

    # "Countless buildings reduced to the skeletal frames of what they once were, stand tall but fragile against the dark sky."
    "Incontables edificios reducidos a los esqueletos de lo que una vez fueron, se alzan altos pero frágiles contra el cielo oscuro."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:299
translate spanish d21a12_71d20c04:

    # "In the middle of it all, a small tower, incongruous, maybe once disguised as an architectural feature, stands solitary and untarnished."
    "En medio de todo, una pequeña torre, incongruente, quizá alguna vez disfrazada como un elemento arquitectónico, se yergue solitaria e intacta."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:302
translate spanish d21a12_95b31903:

    # "The undead city is silent as the three of you move forward."
    "La ciudad no-muerta está en silencio mientras los tres avanzáis."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:303
translate spanish d21a12_0e51423d:

    # "The only sounds that accompany your footsteps shuffling in the dust are the creaking of nearby buildings, disturbed by the wind and the occasional wail of a distant Decayed scavenger."
    "Los únicos sonidos que acompañan el arrastrar de tus pasos en el polvo son los crujidos de los edificios cercanos, agitados por el viento, y el ocasional lamento de un carroñero Decaído a lo lejos."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:306
translate spanish d21a12_602cfe8a:

    # "The elves first follow you, then you notice them fall behind and slow your pace. For you, this place reeks of death and always has. For them, this was home."
    "Las elfas primero te siguen, luego notas que se quedan atrás y ralentizas el paso. Para ti, este lugar apesta a muerte y siempre lo ha hecho. Para ellas, esto fue su hogar."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:309
translate spanish d21a12_2868eabe:

    # I "We... must tread carefully here."
    I "Debemos... andar con cuidado aquí."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:310
translate spanish d21a12_5789fa7f:

    # Z "Is this where it all happened, last time?"
    Z "¿Fue aquí donde pasó todo, la última vez?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:313
translate spanish d21a12_de40aa9b_1:

    # I "...yes."
    I "...sí."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:316
translate spanish d21a12_710682c2:

    # I "I remember them clearly..."
    I "Los recuerdo claramente..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:319
translate spanish d21a12_99bf0575:

    # I "...but it wasn't just them... There were a lot more when it happened."
    I "...pero no eran solo ellos... Había muchos más cuando ocurrió."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:322
translate spanish d21a12_fca091f4:

    # Dec "Hrr... do you see that..."
    Dec "Hrr... ¿veis eso..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:325
translate spanish d21a12_ae8a4236:

    # "With acrid groaning, the Decayed turn their heads towards you..."
    "Con un quejido acre, los Decaídos giran sus cabezas hacia vosotros..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:328
translate spanish d21a12_32daba4a:

    # Z "Murderers. Banished thieves. Broken soldiers. Bereaved widowers. Not every Decayed started their transformation a victim to the change."
    Z "Asesinos. Ladrones desterrados. Soldados rotos. Viudos afligidos. No todos los Decaídos comenzaron su transformación siendo víctimas del cambio."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:329
translate spanish d21a12_a3491fe6:

    # Z "Some chose to be here knowing what they would become."
    Z "Algunos eligieron estar aquí sabiendo lo que llegarían a ser."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:330
translate spanish d21a12_9493aaa7:

    # Z "I know the stories of these men, and why they chose this hell."
    Z "Conozco las historias de estos hombres, y por qué eligieron este infierno."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:333
translate spanish d21a12_a49d3923:

    # "Instinctively, they ready their arms..."
    "Instintivamente, preparan sus armas..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:336
translate spanish d21a12_8eef65cc:

    # I "[persistent.player_name], watch your left."
    I "[persistent.player_name], cuidado con tu izquierda."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:337
translate spanish d21a12_459e73bf:

    # "A figure reveals herself from inside the next building..."
    "Una figura se revela desde el interior del siguiente edificio..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:340
translate spanish d21a12_7623e8a8:

    # Dec "Do you have a death wish, travellers? Because I will not be able to hold these men back for much longer."
    Dec "¿Tenéis algún deseo de muerte, viajeros? Porque no podré contener a estos hombres por mucho más tiempo."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:341
translate spanish d21a12_395e9637:

    # Dec "Should I decide to try in the first place..."
    Dec "Si es que decido intentarlo siquiera..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:344
translate spanish d21a12_b74551c0:

    # Dec "...plenty of meat on you to satisfy the dreaded hunger."
    Dec "... tienes suficiente carne en los huesos para saciar el temido hambre."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:349
translate spanish d21a12_0ae52bd2:

    # Z "Let's get rid of them, [I]. You start with him."
    Z "Vamos a deshacernos de ellos, [I]. Empieza tú con él."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:352
translate spanish d21a12_5018f220_4:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:355
translate spanish d21a12_2071b28c:

    # Dec "What the fuck are you doing down there..."
    Dec "¿Qué cojones estáis haciendo ahí abajo..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:358
translate spanish d21a12_c43281c1:

    # Dec "...wait, is that a..."
    Dec "... espera, ¿eso es un..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:364
translate spanish d21a12_bef22305:

    # Z "Lord Abrax sends his regards. I doubt he would appreciate his soldiers being so undisciplined!"
    Z "Lord Abrax os envía sus saludos. ¡Dudo que le guste que sus soldados sean tan indisciplinados!"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:367
translate spanish d21a12_8934e83c:

    # Dec "Lord Abrax... and what are you then? Another disciple eager to join his cult?!"
    Dec "Lord Abrax... ¿y tú qué eres entonces? ¿Otro discípulo deseoso de unirse a su culto?!"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:368
translate spanish d21a12_38939c20:

    # Dec "If those women are your tribute, we would... happily accept."
    Dec "Si esas mujeres son tu tributo, las... aceptaríamos con gusto."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:371
translate spanish d21a12_b6adf4d6:

    # Dec "...but if you are looking to turn, then we won't help you."
    Dec "... pero si buscas convertirte, entonces no te ayudaremos."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:372
translate spanish d21a12_751c9ce8:

    # Dec "This is not his territory, here. We are not his puppets."
    Dec "Esto no es su territorio, aquí. No somos sus marionetas."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:378
translate spanish d21a12_ef6d359e:

    # Z "Get ready, [I]. We will make this quick."
    Z "Prepárate, [I]. Esto será rápido."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:381
translate spanish d21a12_5018f220_5:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:384
translate spanish d21a12_a8099415:

    # Z "Tributes, you say?"
    Z "¿Tributos, dices?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:387
translate spanish d21a12_444d3f83:

    # Z "As you wish... here's one."
    Z "Como deseéis... aquí tenéis uno."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:392
translate spanish d21a12_64c8e7d0:

    # Z "I was his apprentice, once..."
    Z "Fui su aprendiz, una vez..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:395
translate spanish d21a12_0cf06034:

    # I "...?"
    I "¿...?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:396
translate spanish d21a12_f2a01647:

    # Z "If any part of that rotten brain of yours is still working, do the smart thing and let us through."
    Z "Si alguna parte de ese cerebro podrido tuyo sigue funcionando, haz lo inteligente y déjanos pasar."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:397
translate spanish d21a12_46cc8994:

    # Z "I will tell him to spare you and your tribe. Attack us, and you will die."
    Z "Le diré que os perdone a ti y a tu tribu. Atacadnos, y moriréis."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:398
translate spanish d21a12_2f79b242:

    # Z "...either by our hands, or by those of his men."
    Z "...ya sea por nuestras manos, o por las de sus hombres."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:401
translate spanish d21a12_0d7a42e3:

    # Dec "You? Lord Abrax's disciple? Give me a reason to believe you have spoken to him..."
    Dec "¿Tú? ¿Discípulo de Lord Abrax? Dame una razón para creer que has hablado con él..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:402
translate spanish d21a12_74055648:

    # Z "Have you been to his personal chambers? Have you seen him seated in power, his two women to his side?"
    Z "¿Has estado en sus aposentos personales? ¿Lo has visto sentado en el poder, con sus dos mujeres a su lado?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:403
translate spanish d21a12_1521dc97:

    # Z "I have. That and more."
    Z "Lo he visto. Eso y más."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:404
translate spanish d21a12_181b791f:

    # Z "But then, I knew him well, from the time before his ascension. That's one reason he let me go unharmed. You don't want to find out the other."
    Z "Pero es que lo conocía bien, de la época anterior a su ascenso. Esa es una razón por la que me dejó marchar ileso. No quieres saber cuál es la otra."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:407
translate spanish d21a12_0a1d1e44:

    # Dec "His... chambers."
    Dec "Sus... aposentos."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:408
translate spanish d21a12_5b893110:

    # Dec "You... you aren't bluffing."
    Dec "Tú... no estás faroleando."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:411
translate spanish d21a12_638825be:

    # Dec "Men... {i}*sighs*{/i}"
    Dec "Hombres... {i}*suspiros*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:412
translate spanish d21a12_241208e0:

    # Dec "Stand aside. There shall be no fighting, today."
    Dec "Apartaos. Hoy no habrá lucha."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:418
translate spanish d21a12_2e05fafa:

    # Z "Come, you two. Let's not wait for them to change their minds."
    Z "Vamos, vosotras dos. No esperemos a que cambien de opinión."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:421
translate spanish d21a12_51607195_1:

    # So "..."
    So "..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:440
translate spanish d21a64_06557184:

    # Z "Well done. Now turn around; they're coming."
    Z "Bien hecho. Ahora daos la vuelta; vienen."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:443
translate spanish d21a64_37154df3:

    # "A feral growl rises as the decayed march toward you..."
    "Un gruñido salvaje se alza mientras los Decaídos marchan hacia vosotros..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:446
translate spanish d21a64_6962c355:

    # I "I'm taking the slow ones."
    I "Yo me encargo de los lentos."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:450
translate spanish d21a64_7a1fe065:

    # "As you fight your way through the crowd..."
    "Mientras te abres paso entre la multitud..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:455
translate spanish d21a64_51607195:

    # So "..."
    So "..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:456
translate spanish d21a64_f942a1b7:

    # Z "Sonmi, stay close as we get through them, before others show up!"
    Z "¡Sonmi, mantente cerca mientras los atravesamos, antes de que aparezcan más!"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:462
translate spanish d21a71x_773259b2:

    # Z "Sonmi!..."
    Z "¡Sonmi!..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:465
translate spanish d21a71x_47ab387c:

    # C "I'm... so... hungry..."
    C "Tengo... tanta... hambre..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:468
translate spanish d21a71x_057e4259:

    # C "Please... Sonmi..."
    C "Por favor... Sonmi..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:471
translate spanish d21a71x_a50d7b5d:

    # Decm "That... is your name, is it not?"
    Decm "Ese... es tu nombre, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:474
translate spanish d21a71x_72c59413:

    # Decm "Please... I know..."
    Decm "Por favor... sé..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:475
translate spanish d21a71x_b48d8a09:

    # Decm "...that you have food in there."
    Decm "...que tienes comida ahí dentro."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:478
translate spanish d21a71x_b5e3f821:

    # So "I..."
    So "Yo..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:481
translate spanish d21a71x_b7bd0e7d:

    # So "I'm sorry, but I can't..."
    So "Lo siento, pero no puedo..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:482
translate spanish d21a71x_b39aee90:

    # Al "Sonmi, h-he knows your name?"
    Al "Sonmi, ¿él-él sabe tu nombre?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:485
translate spanish d21a71x_63e2b98c:

    # Al "Please. I don't know who this is..."
    Al "Por favor. No sé quién es este..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:488
translate spanish d21a71x_6c64404e:

    # Al "...but we need to leave, now."
    Al "...pero tenemos que irnos, ahora."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:491
translate spanish d21a71x_38f1609b:

    # Al "We are not safe out here. Please, think of Lunai."
    Al "No estamos seguros aquí fuera. Por favor, piensa en Lunai."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:492
translate spanish d21a71x_4d7c248b:

    # Lu "..."
    Lu "..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:503
translate spanish d21a71x_f70d2cc3:

    # "As you enter the tower, you are reminded of the similar entrance to the bunker where the mutants live."
    "Al entrar en la torre, te recuerda a la entrada similar del búnker donde viven los mutantes."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:504
translate spanish d21a71x_6fa35444:

    # "You recognize the pattern of ramshackle surroundings, the large somewhat rusty but still sealed gate..."
    "Reconoces el patrón de los alrededores destartalados, la gran puerta algo oxidada pero aún sellada..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:505
translate spanish d21a71x_9aeaae59:

    # "...and just like when you first followed her, the short-haired elf is approaching what appears to be a switch."
    "...y justo como cuando la seguiste por primera vez, la elfa de pelo corto se acerca a lo que parece ser un interruptor."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:508
translate spanish d21a71x_79c5f037:

    # "[I] and Sonmi are silent, almost solemn, as they take in the surroundings..."
    "[I] y Sonmi están en silencio, casi solemnes, mientras observan el entorno..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:511
translate spanish d21a71x_321920fa:

    # "...a place they have not dared to come to for more than eighty years."
    "...un lugar al que no se han atrevido a venir en más de ochenta años."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:531
translate spanish d21a71x_cd0332b9:

    # "As the large vault door opens, the three of you forget to breathe for a moment, as you take in the environment."
    "Mientras se abre la gran puerta acorazada, los tres contienen la respiración un momento, al contemplar el entorno."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:533
translate spanish d21a71x_25f28454:

    # "A thick layer of dust and a dry sense of stuffy decay fill the air, debris and remains of a different time are scattered everywhere."
    "Una gruesa capa de polvo y una sensación seca de decadencia apolillada llenan el aire, escombros y restos de otra época están esparcidos por todas partes."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:534
translate spanish d21a71x_d6472ce8:

    # "For you, this place is long abandoned. But your two companions see so much more."
    "Para ti, este lugar lleva mucho tiempo abandonado. Pero tus dos compañeras ven mucho más."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:535
translate spanish d21a71x_466a7d85:

    # "And for a moment, the white-haired girl's breathing becomes quick and shallow."
    "Y por un momento, la respiración de la chica de pelo blanco se vuelve rápida y superficial."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:549
translate spanish d21a71x_51607195:

    # So "..."
    So "..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:553
translate spanish d21a71x_c6b9e3b8:

    # "Once that sense of urgent breathing passes, the silence is deafening. Finally you see the source of her distress..."
    "Una vez que pasa esa sensación de respiración angustiosa, el silencio es ensordecedor. Finalmente ves la fuente de su angustia..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:557
translate spanish d21a71x_a4cb57c3:

    # "You step forward, approaching the withered corpse."
    "Das un paso adelante, acercándote al cadáver momificado."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:561
translate spanish d21a71x_02445104:

    # "It's mouth open, and face twisted, you recognize the ears."
    "Con la boca abierta y el rostro torcido, reconoces las orejas."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:562
translate spanish d21a71x_c6214d3e:

    # "Even after all this time, the clear marks of stab wounds and dried blood spatters make it obvious that his death must have been painful and tragic."
    "Incluso después de todo este tiempo, las claras marcas de puñaladas y los salpicaduras de sangre seca hacen evidente que su muerte debió ser dolorosa y trágica."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:565
translate spanish d21a71x_17c17d8b:

    # "Sonmi and you stand before it, and you notice a slight trembling in her hands, as her gaze is fixed on someone who was once family to her."
    "Sonmi y tú estáis ante él, y notas un ligero temblor en sus manos, mientras su mirada se fija en alguien que una vez fue su familia."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:568
translate spanish d21a71x_5018f220:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:579
translate spanish d21a71x_5210bcfa:

    # "She presses a button, and you notice the heavy steel walls behind you start to move..."
    "Pulsa un botón, y notas que los pesados muros de acero detrás de ti empiezan a moverse..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:591
translate spanish d21a71x_d003a97e:

    # I "{i}*gasps*{/i}"
    I "{i}*jadea*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:595
translate spanish d21a71x_0b9f166a:

    # "With the door in front of her open, [I] sharply inhales, before pausing..."
    "Con la puerta frente a ella abierta, [I] inhala bruscamente, antes de detenerse..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:599
translate spanish d21a71x_da6f688a:

    # I "Sonmi, you..."
    I "Sonmi, tú..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:602
translate spanish d21a71x_e1cb6d3b:

    # I "...you don't have to go in there."
    I "...no tienes que entrar ahí."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:605
translate spanish d21a71x_38cbb479:

    # So "...?"
    So "...?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:611
translate spanish d21a71x_cdc135df:

    # I "I'm sorry..."
    I "Lo siento..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:616
translate spanish d21a71x_5c4372f1:

    # I "...but there is nothing left."
    I "...pero no queda nada."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:619
translate spanish d21a71x_51607195_1:

    # So "..."
    So "..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:630
translate spanish d21a71x_4eb212a1:

    # "She stares at the old chairs. Those which she described in explicit detail in her writings."
    "Mira las viejas sillas. Esas que describió con todo lujo de detalle en sus escritos."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:633
translate spanish d21a71x_205ce0e8:

    # "The centerpiece, the tangible evidence and reminder of that one moment in time that changed her life forever."
    "La pieza central, la evidencia tangible y el recordatorio de ese momento en el tiempo que cambió su vida para siempre."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:636
translate spanish d21a71x_51607195_2:

    # So "..."
    So "..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:643
translate spanish d21a71x_51607195_3:

    # So "..."
    So "..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:650
translate spanish d21a71x_40123e6c:

    # So "I want you back..."
    So "Quiero que vuelvas..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:660
translate spanish d21a71x_2963f082:

    # So "I want you back... {i}*sniff*{/i}"
    So "Quiero que vuelvas... {i}*resopla*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:661
translate spanish d21a71x_1c076e6d:

    # So "Please... oh please... Aloi... Lunai..."
    So "Por favor... oh por favor... Aloi... Lunai..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:664
translate spanish d21a71x_07b0d935:

    # So "Please.... it's not right... {i}*sobs*{/i}"
    So "Por favor... no es justo... {i}*sollozos*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:667
translate spanish d21a71x_8ef185b3:

    # So "...Please don't hurt him."
    So "...Por favor, no le hagas daño."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:668
translate spanish d21a71x_1d64b9d9:

    # So "I beg of you!"
    So "¡Te lo suplico!"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:672
translate spanish d21a71x_a52ef619:

    # So "Aaah!"
    So "¡Aaah!"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:673
translate spanish d21a71x_d18b611a:

    # Decm "Keep your head up, girl!"
    Decm "¡Mantén la cabeza en alto, muchacha!"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:676
translate spanish d21a71x_ecb2e069:

    # So "Please, please don't hurt him. I will do anything... not him!"
    So "Por favor, por favor no le hagas daño. Haré lo que sea... ¡a él no!"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:679
translate spanish d21a71x_b6d8df3c:

    # Decm "He's that important to you, huh?!"
    Decm "¿Tan importante es para ti, eh?!"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:682
translate spanish d21a71x_8a28c15f:

    # Decm "Yeah... I remember him. He was the one telling you to get back inside..."
    Decm "Sí... lo recuerdo. Él era el que te decía que volvieras a entrar..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:685
translate spanish d21a71x_715e2f0d:

    # Decm "Back underground, like the cockroach he is..."
    Decm "De vuelta al subsuelo, como la cucaracha que es..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:688
translate spanish d21a71x_ff5030f5:

    # Decm "Should've let us in here, you two."
    Decm "Deberíais habernos dejado entrar aquí, vosotros dos."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:689
translate spanish d21a71x_861a9919:

    # Decm "Shouldn't have been showing off, with your clean faces, your full bellies..."
    Decm "No deberíais estar presumiendo, con vuestras caras limpias, vuestros vientres llenos..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:690
translate spanish d21a71x_47a05b65:

    # Decm "...had your own perfect bunker in here all along, but were too good to share though, all this time."
    Decm "...tuvisteis vuestro propio búnker perfecto aquí dentro todo este tiempo, pero erais demasiado buenos para compartir, durante todo este tiempo."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:693
translate spanish d21a71x_1eb37ce0:

    # Al "Sonmi, I'm sorry it came to this. Please don't think this is your fault."
    Al "Sonmi, siento que haya llegado a esto. Por favor, no pienses que es tu culpa."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:696
translate spanish d21a71x_e775469d:

    # Al "I love you, and always will. And I will see you again, on the other side."
    Al "Te quiero, y siempre lo haré. Y te veré de nuevo, al otro lado."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:697
translate spanish d21a71x_ca75449d:

    # Decm "See you on the other side, ay?! And what if there ain't nothing after this? {i}*laughs*{/i}"
    Decm "¿¡Al otro lado, eh?! ¿Y si no hay nada después de esto? {i}*risas*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:700
translate spanish d21a71x_20957a83:

    # So "No... please. He doesn't deserve this..."
    So "No... por favor. Él no merece esto..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:701
translate spanish d21a71x_1a1e6a58:

    # Decm "Don't {i}deserve{/i}?!"
    Decm "¿Qué no {i}merece{/i}?!"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:704
translate spanish d21a71x_412a33a2:

    # Decm "I'll tell you what, little flower. There's nothing you deserve."
    Decm "Te diré una cosa, florecita. No mereces nada."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:705
translate spanish d21a71x_128786eb:

    # Decm "Look at us! Do you think we deserve to have our skin rot in this hellscape of a city?"
    Decm "¡Míranos! ¿Crees que merecemos que nuestra piel se pudra en este infierno de ciudad?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:708
translate spanish d21a71x_2ae8dba3:

    # Decm "No. The only thing you deserve, is DEATH. The weak are meat, nothing else!"
    Decm "No. Lo único que mereces es la MUERTE. Los débiles son carne, ¡nada más!"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:711
translate spanish d21a71x_a40324e3:

    # Decm "Now open your eyes, and watch the fruit of your choices. Only you were brave and stupid enough."
    Decm "Ahora abre los ojos y mira el fruto de tus decisiones. Solo tú fuiste lo bastante valiente y estúpida."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:714
translate spanish d21a71x_bdaef3d8:

    # Al "Don't ever forget, Sonmi. Death is just another path."
    Al "No lo olvides nunca, Sonmi. La muerte es solo otro camino."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:719
translate spanish d21a71x_e50d1f6e:

