    So "P-por favor, háblame. Por favor... por favor..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:770
translate spanish d21a71x_550c1bb0:

    # Decm "Looks like your friend is gone, girl."
    Decm "Parece que tu amigo se ha ido, muchacha."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:773
translate spanish d21a71x_b9399fef:

    # Decm "...and you're soon to join him! But before that, let us see who else we caught in these halls, shall we?"
    Decm "...¡y pronto le seguirás! Pero antes, veamos a quién más atrapamos en estos pasillos, ¿eh?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:776
translate spanish d21a71x_0a41539c:

    # Decm "...you spoiled, ignorant elven freak."
    Decm "… bicho elfo, malcriada e ignorante."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:779
translate spanish d21a71x_53599661:

    # Decm "HELP ME CARRY HER..."
    Decm "AYÚDAME A LLEVARLA..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:783
translate spanish d21a71x_c541d1b2:

    # Decm "There!"
    Decm "¡Ahí!"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:784
translate spanish d21a71x_479c8f35:

    # Decm "This is where meatbags like you belongs."
    Decm "Aquí es donde pertenecen los sacos de carne como tú."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:787
translate spanish d21a71x_ffea152d:

    # Decm "Boss, we've found one more."
    Decm "Jefe, hemos encontrado una más."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:788
translate spanish d21a71x_a01685a8:

    # C "W-where are you taking me...?"
    C "¿D-dónde me lleváis...?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:790
translate spanish d21a71x_4c0ada4e:

    # C "Ah! P-please let me go!"
    C "¡Ah! ¡P-por favor, suéltame!"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:791
translate spanish d21a71x_ce287d46:

    # So "No..."
    So "No..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:794
translate spanish d21a71x_fa87a8ca:

    # Lu "S-sonmi? Where is Aloi? W-what do we do?!"
    Lu "¿S-sonmi? ¿Dónde está Aloi? ¿Q-qué hacemos?!"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:795
translate spanish d21a71x_09b6559d:

    # Decm "More fresh meat!"
    Decm "¡Más carne fresca!"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:798
translate spanish d21a71x_9c7c0b62:

    # Lu "Sister, why are you looking like this? What are they doing to us?"
    Lu "Hermana, ¿por qué estás así? ¿Qué nos están haciendo?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:801
translate spanish d21a71x_565362f5:

    # So "I... I am so sorry..."
    So "Yo... lo siento tanto..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:802
translate spanish d21a71x_a5f96e76:

    # So "...for everything."
    So "...por todo."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:805
translate spanish d21a71x_a4b8632e:

    # Decm "How do they keep this clean and smooth..."
    Decm "Cómo mantienen esto limpio y suave..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:808
translate spanish d21a71x_66fb0359:

    # Decm "Can't believe I'd end up doing this, but she's gonna keep me fed for a long while!"
    Decm "No puedo creer que vaya a terminar haciendo esto, ¡pero ella me va a mantener alimentado durante un buen tiempo!"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:811
translate spanish d21a71x_c79edbee:

    # Decm "Get to work, you freak! Let's get the meat and leave."
    Decm "¡Ponte a trabajar, bicho! Cogemos la carne y nos vamos."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:814
translate spanish d21a71x_60149961:

    # Decm "One clean chop will do the trick!"
    Decm "¡Un tajo limpio será suficiente!"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:815
translate spanish d21a71x_16d76c12:

    # Lu "W-what are you..."
    Lu "Q-qué estáis..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:818
translate spanish d21a71x_0606f5a1:

    # So "Please, don't... not her..."
    So "Por favor, no... a ella no..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:819
translate spanish d21a71x_cc373aaa:

    # So "...out of anyone... please not Lunai. Take me!"
    So "...de todas... por favor, a Lunai no. ¡Llevadme a mí!"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:822
translate spanish d21a71x_c95be0df:

    # Decm "Shut up! You know begging won't help!"
    Decm "¡Cállate! ¡Sabes que rogar no ayuda!"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:825
translate spanish d21a71x_d0796fd0:

    # Lu "W-why are you looking like that, are they... going to do something bad?"
    Lu "P-por qué estás así, ¿van a... hacer algo malo?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:826
translate spanish d21a71x_aa0afbcb:

    # So "Not Lunai... I'm begging you..."
    So "A Lunai no... te lo suplico..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:828
translate spanish d21a71x_db3af69b:

    # Lu "Sonmi... I'm scared!"
    Lu "¡Sonmi... tengo miedo!"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:839
translate spanish d21a71x_4d7c248b_1:

    # Lu "..."
    Lu "..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:852
translate spanish d21a71x_51607195_4:

    # So "..."
    So "..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:869
translate spanish d21a71x_bebd368f:

    # Decm "Finally silent, girl?"
    Decm "¿Por fin en silencio, muchacha?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:870
translate spanish d21a71x_c4efc59b:

    # Decm "Good. I like it when they don't resist."
    Decm "Bien. Me gusta cuando no oponen resistencia."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:873
translate spanish d21a71x_e70194de:

    # Decm "I'm going to... ngh... take off these clothes before you can join your friends."
    Decm "Voy a... ngh... quitarte esta ropa antes de que puedas reunirte con tus amigos."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:876
translate spanish d21a71x_29f73ab1:

    # Decm "That's what you believe in, don't you? Seeing someone in the next life and what not?"
    Decm "En eso crees, ¿verdad? ¿Ver a alguien en la otra vida y esas cosas?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:877
translate spanish d21a71x_6fd074fc:

    # Decm "Tsk... maybe you're right. Maybe we all deserve a better life."
    Decm "Tsk... quizá tengas razón. Quizá todos merecemos una vida mejor."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:882
translate spanish d21a71x_1f46ca42:

    # Decm "Now, what you don't deserve, is an easy death, if you don't stop cramping up!!"
    Decm "Ahora, lo que no mereces, es una muerte fácil, ¡si no dejas de tensarte!"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:886
translate spanish d21a71x_51607195_5:

    # So "..."
    So "..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:887
translate spanish d21a71x_fce85176:

    # Decm "Let me take off these clothes, do you hear me?!"
    Decm "¡Déjame quitarte esta ropa, ¿me oyes?!"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:890
translate spanish d21a71x_068c7dde:

    # Decm "Why do you have to make it so damn hard. Just... nh..."
    Decm "¿Por qué tienes que ponerlo tan malditamente difícil? Solo... nh..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:893
translate spanish d21a71x_64f06fae:

    # Decm "Ah, you know what, fuck it. I might as well just finish you off."
    Decm "Ah, ¿sabes qué? A la mierda. Mejor te remato."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:896
translate spanish d21a71x_485cf407:

    # Decm "Your journey is over, stupid girl. It's been real nice of you to show us the way in."
    Decm "Tu viaje ha terminado, estúpida muchacha. Ha sido muy amable por tu parte mostrarnos el camino de entrada."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:899
translate spanish d21a71x_9b52179e:

    # Decm "Putting up with your lectures was rough. But it was worth it in the end. We've got what we wanted."
    Decm "Aguantar tus sermones fue duro. Pero mereció la pena al final. Conseguimos lo que queríamos."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:900
translate spanish d21a71x_f41f0b27:

    # Decm "Now, see you on the other side."
    Decm "Ahora, nos vemos al otro lado."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:908
translate spanish d21a71x_380838ca:

    # Decm "M-Malik?... What happe-"
    Decm "¿M-Malik?... ¿Qué ha pa-"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:912
translate spanish d21a71x_54007c74:

    # Decm "What is going on?!"
    Decm "¡¿Qué está pasando?!"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:920
translate spanish d21a71x_94e4b06e:

    # Decm "Nkgh... agh..."
    Decm "Nkgh... agh..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:923
translate spanish d21a71x_ead13045:

    # Decm "{i}*exhales*{/i}"
    Decm "{i}*exhala*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:926
translate spanish d21a71x_e1a57455:

    # Yu "Murderers..."
    Yu "Asesinos..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:929
translate spanish d21a71x_6c527f19:

    # Yu "S-Sonmi.. is that you?"
    Yu "¿S-Sonmi... eres tú?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:932
translate spanish d21a71x_9d2f62a7:

    # Yu "Did they hurt you?! The others, they are..."
    Yu "¡¿Te han hecho daño?! Los demás, están..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:935
translate spanish d21a71x_5395930c:

    # Yu "Where is Lu-..."
    Yu "¿Dónde está Lu-..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:938
translate spanish d21a71x_67646bbd:

    # Yu "{i}*gasps in terror*{/i}"
    Yu "{i}*jadeos de terror*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:939
translate spanish d21a71x_fc8caa4d:

    # Yu "No..."
    Yu "No..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:945
translate spanish d21a71x_ff359040:

    # Yu "Sonmi. You need to be strong now. We need to run fast..."
    Yu "Sonmi. Tienes que ser fuerte ahora. Tenemos que correr rápido..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:946
translate spanish d21a71x_dc0bd124:

    # Yu "...and far, far away from here!"
    Yu "… ¡y muy, muy lejos de aquí!"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:950
translate spanish d21a71x_fbd527f6:

    # So "Please... come back..."
    So "Por favor... volved..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:951
translate spanish d21a71x_228cd094:

    # So "{i}*whimpers*{/i}"
    So "{i}*gimoteos*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:954
translate spanish d21a71x_8c042929:

    # So "That's all... I want."
    So "Solo eso... quiero."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:957
translate spanish d21a71x_c8da07e1:

    # So "I am sorry for talking to them. I am sorry. They followed me home."
    So "Siento haber hablado con ellos. Lo siento. Me siguieron hasta casa."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:960
translate spanish d21a71x_3c75f6b9:

    # So "I am sorry I was so naive. Please, come back to me, please!!"
    So "Siento haber sido tan ingenua. ¡Por favor, volved a mí, por favor!"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:963
translate spanish d21a71x_4421307e:

    # So "You didn't deserve it... They should have taken me instead."
    So "No lo merecíais... Deberían haberme llevado a mí."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:964
translate spanish d21a71x_a8a2a99f:

    # "She cries out..."
    "Ella grita..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:965
translate spanish d21a71x_5018f220_1:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:968
translate spanish d21a71x_e7e4ceb1:

    # I "I'm sorry, but I must go to her."
    I "Lo siento, pero debo ir a su lado."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:969
translate spanish d21a71x_0643f377:

    # I "There is something... I'd like you to bring me."
    I "Hay algo... que me gustaría que me trajeras."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:970
translate spanish d21a71x_31e5093c:

    # I "You will know what I mean. Take a look at the device. It should still work."
    I "Sabrás a lo que me refiero. Échale un vistazo al dispositivo. Todavía debería funcionar."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:975
translate spanish d21a71x_3ead8c68:

    # "You look to your right, and notice a device similar to the one in [I]'s hideout..."
    "Miras a tu derecha y ves un dispositivo similar al del escondite de [I]..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:978
translate spanish d21a71x_ba296e9b:

    # I "Come here, Sonmi."
    I "Ven aquí, Sonmi."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:981
translate spanish d21a71x_6435950f:

    # So "{i}*sobs*{/i} Can we really not bring them back, Yuna?"
    So "{i}*sollozos*{/i} ¿De verdad no podemos traerlos de vuelta, Yuna?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:982
translate spanish d21a71x_e54605c8:

    # I "You know this... We can't..."
    I "Lo sabes... No podemos..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:985
translate spanish d21a71x_a9cfd08c:

    # So "...I still miss them so much."
    So "...Todavía los echo tanto de menos."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:986
translate spanish d21a71x_5018f220_2:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:989
translate spanish d21a71x_375a1589:

    # "The two of them share a moment together, and Sonmi's crying eventually turns into a quiet sobbing..."
    "Las dos comparten un momento juntas, y el llanto de Sonmi acaba convirtiéndose en un sollozo silencioso..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:992
translate spanish d21a71x_321ee7cf:

    # "You quietly approach the device in the meantime, wondering what [I] meant for you to bring her."
    "Mientras tanto, te acercas silenciosamente al dispositivo, preguntándote qué quería [I] que le trajeras."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:996
translate spanish d21a71x_d7162fa8:

    # Z "How to start this thing..."
    Z "Cómo se enciende esto..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1009
translate spanish d21a127_85ae780a:

    # Zt "This message is not for me to open."
    Zt "Este mensaje no es para que yo lo abra."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1017
translate spanish d21a127_1d7454b2:

    # "With the tab in your hand, you walk over to [I]..."
    "Con la tableta en la mano, te acercas a [I]..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1020
translate spanish d21a127_25cb7801:

    # Z "I think this is what you wanted."
    Z "Creo que esto es lo que querías."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1023
translate spanish d21a127_5018f220:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1027
translate spanish d21a127_5018f220_1:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1028
translate spanish d21a127_b8b0b563:

    # "Her eyes lighten up..."
    "Sus ojos se iluminan..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1031
translate spanish d21a127_5018f220_2:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1034
translate spanish d21a127_1192e6c6:

    # I "Yes, this is what I was searching for. Thank you."
    I "Sí, esto es lo que estaba buscando. Gracias."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1037
translate spanish d21a127_3f745bcf:

    # I "Sonmi, look, this is why I brought us here."
    I "Sonmi, mira, por esto nos traje aquí."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1038
translate spanish d21a127_20541abf:

    # I "A message from Aloi, to you."
    I "Un mensaje de Aloi, para ti."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1047
translate spanish d21a127_51607195:

    # So "..."
    So "..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1051
translate spanish d21a127_46787122:

    # So "{i}*gasps*{/i}"
    So "{i}*jadea*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1052
translate spanish d21a127_b7bc43b7:

    # So "It's..."
    So "Es..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1055
translate spanish d21a127_41f3eddd:

    # So "...it's really him."
    So "...es realmente él."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1061
translate spanish d21a127_b2a9c550:

    # So "He... really wrote this..."
    So "Él... realmente escribió esto..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1062
translate spanish d21a127_283277d4:

    # I "He did. And he wanted me to give it to you, when the time was right."
    I "Sí. Y quería que te lo diera cuando llegara el momento."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1065
translate spanish d21a127_2e4ad101:

    # "The two of them read the message together, and for the first time, you see a faint smile cross the stern features of the white haired elf."
    "Las dos leen el mensaje juntas, y por primera vez, ves una leve sonrisa cruzar los severos rasgos de la elfa de pelo blanco."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1066
translate spanish d21a127_1510bdd8:

    # "You step outside the room, granting them the privacy of this moment, that you recognise being for them only..."
    "Sales de la habitación, concediéndoles la privacidad de este momento, que reconoces que es solo para ellas..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1067
translate spanish d21a127_822be3e9:

    # "...and wait until the time comes to travel back to the hideout."
    "...y esperas hasta que llega el momento de volver al escondite."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1076
translate spanish d21a127_b494f841:

    # So "I'm leaving, Yuna."
    So "Me voy, Yuna."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1079
translate spanish d21a127_f5e25852:

    # I "But... we just came back from there... are you sure, that...-"
    I "Pero... acabamos de volver de allí... ¿estás segura, de que...-"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1082
translate spanish d21a127_400dd709:

    # So "I am."
    So "Lo estoy."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1085
translate spanish d21a127_f36de544:

    # So "And don't come looking for me."
    So "Y no vengas a buscarme."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1088
translate spanish d21a127_2c0f6f29:

    # So "Whatever happens."
    So "Pase lo que pase."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1091
translate spanish d21a127_38ebe3e8:

    # I "But Sonmi, I..."
    I "Pero Sonmi, yo..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1094
translate spanish d21a127_29a9d014:

    # So "I'm sorry, Yuna."
    So "Lo siento, Yuna."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1097
translate spanish d21a127_108b0619:

    # "She turns around and leaves..."
    "Se da la vuelta y se marcha..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1100
translate spanish d21a127_5490477a:

    # I "Why do I have a feeling that it's different, this time..."
    I "¿Por qué tengo la sensación de que esta vez es diferente..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1103
translate spanish d21a127_d5ae0700:

    # I "...do you want to stay a little longer?"
    I "...¿quieres quedarte un poco más?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1108
translate spanish d21a127_bb62e181:

    # Z "Gladly."
    Z "Con gusto."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1113
translate spanish d21a127_83c97f36:

    # Z "I can stay for a while, yes."
    Z "Puedo quedarme un rato, sí."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1120
translate spanish d21a127_64e6d705:

    # I "We can go up there, if you want?"
    I "Podemos subir allí, ¿si quieres?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1123
translate spanish d21a127_ba2854a0:

    # I "I will be with you in a few minutes, if that is okay."
    I "Estaré contigo en unos minutos, si te parece bien."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1127
translate spanish d21a127_ed7c6e28:

    # "Twenty minutes later..."
    "Veinte minutos después..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1132
translate spanish d21a127_d67fc550:

    # Zt "This place is beautiful..."
    Zt "Este lugar es precioso..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1133
translate spanish d21a127_33c17643:

    # I "Are you not scared of heights?"
    I "¿No te dan miedo las alturas?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1136
translate spanish d21a127_7eba1e7d:

    # Z "I have had to climb entire pyramids before. This is different, but not undoable."
    Z "He tenido que escalar pirámides enteras antes. Esto es diferente, pero no imposible."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1137
translate spanish d21a127_1711a043:

    # I "{i}*giggles*{/i} "
    I "{i}*risitas*{/i} "

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1140
translate spanish d21a127_59302871:

    # I "Then we share a similar fate. Sonmi loved to climb the tallest of towers."
    I "Entonces compartimos un destino similar. A Sonmi le encantaba escalar las torres más altas."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1143
translate spanish d21a127_d93978ce:

    # I "And she'd try to balance her steps like this. It never not made me worry!"
    I "Y solía intentar equilibrar sus pasos así. ¡Siempre me preocupaba!"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1144
translate spanish d21a127_7dad8412:

    # I "It requires only one single step to expose our fragility."
    I "Solo hace falta un solo paso para exponer nuestra fragilidad."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1147
translate spanish d21a127_23aa797b:

    # I "To be fair, she got really good at it. And she always had a big smile when climbing!"
    I "Para ser justos, se le daba muy bien. ¡Y siempre tenía una gran sonrisa cuando escalaba!"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1148
translate spanish d21a127_bc2dc5f7:

    # I "But... those times are over."
    I "Pero... esos tiempos han pasado."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1151
translate spanish d21a127_54f20479:

    # I "Everything eventually changes, one way or another."
    I "Todo acaba cambiando, de una forma u otra."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1157
translate spanish d21a127_8754f37d:

    # "She sits down next to you..."
    "Se sienta a tu lado..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1160
translate spanish d21a127_5018f220_3:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1161
translate spanish d21a127_aedf4ebf:

    # Z "You're very resilient."
    Z "Eres muy resistente."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1162
translate spanish d21a127_e4e98734:

    # I "Me? What makes you say that?"
    I "¿Yo? ¿Qué te hace decir eso?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1163
translate spanish d21a127_cc9297d9:

    # Z "I've seen it ever since you left my house."
    Z "Lo he visto desde que saliste de mi casa."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1166
translate spanish d21a127_00c1e849:

    # Z "Always moving forward, always focused on what's next."
    Z "Siempre avanzando, siempre centrada en lo que viene después."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1167
translate spanish d21a127_858ea291:

    # Z "The decayed didn't get to you."
    Z "Los Decaídos no pudieron contigo."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1168
translate spanish d21a127_dbe426d9:

    # Z "You found Fangs. Built a place for yourself among strangers."
    Z "Encontraste a Fangs. Construiste un lugar para ti entre extraños."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1169
translate spanish d21a127_a8366278:

    # Z "And now you're asking me to help your friend."
    Z "Y ahora me pides que ayude a tu amiga."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1170
translate spanish d21a127_44f0f122:

    # Z "Who depends on you, too."
    Z "Que también depende de ti."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1173
translate spanish d21a127_5018f220_4:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1176
translate spanish d21a127_f63d310e:

    # I "Sometimes it feels like looking after family."
    I "A veces se siente como cuidar de la familia."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1177
translate spanish d21a127_3ea831c4:

    # I "But you know more about that than me."
    I "Pero tú sabes más de eso que yo."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1180
translate spanish d21a127_b70c19cf:

    # "She giggles quietly..."
    "Ríe suavemente..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1181
translate spanish d21a127_1c3e6b19:

    # Z "Would I?"
    Z "¿Ah, sí?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1182
translate spanish d21a127_4fbfd4cc:

    # Z "How long has it been since you found the first tower? A hundred years?"
    Z "¿Cuánto tiempo ha pasado desde que encontraste la primera torre? ¿Cien años?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1185
translate spanish d21a127_9d73ac5a:

    # I "I..."
    I "Yo..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1188
translate spanish d21a127_c19ac202:

    # "She smiles..."
    "Sonríe..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1191
translate spanish d21a127_5d75792b:

    # I "Probably... yes."
    I "Probablemente... sí."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1198
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_53f8c3b3:

    # Z "...and you never seem to have lost that resilience. Why is that?"
    Z "...y nunca pareces haber perdido esa resistencia. ¿Por qué?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1199
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_5018f220:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1200
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_34b40d47:

    # "She takes her time answering."
    "Se toma su tiempo para responder."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1203
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_808a8abd:

    # I "Because every challenge I've ever faced eventually became a memory."
    I "Porque cada desafío al que me he enfrentado acabó convirtiéndose en un recuerdo."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1206
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_3553c07f:

    # Z "A memory?"
    Z "¿Un recuerdo?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1209
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_80d05949:

    # I "At the time, it always feels like the end."
    I "En ese momento, siempre parece el final."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1210
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_2e7bd9ed:

    # I "Then a year passes. Ten years. Fifty."
    I "Luego pasa un año. Diez años. Cincuenta."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1211
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_09969604:

    # I "And one day you wake up and realise it's something else keeping you awake at night. Some new challenge."
    I "Y un día te despiertas y te das cuenta de que es otra cosa la que te mantiene despierto por la noche. Algún nuevo desafío."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1212
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_c13607f2:

    # I "The old wound is still there... it just doesn't hurt the same."
    I "La vieja herida sigue ahí... solo que ya no duele igual."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1213
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_86bb784b:

    # Z "And Sonmi can't move on? It has been a lifetime."
    Z "¿Y Sonmi no puede seguir adelante? Ha pasado toda una vida."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1214
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_3143d526:

    # I "For you, it has."
    I "Para ti, sí."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1217
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_6cb285bd:

    # I "For her... the pain is still strong."
    I "Para ella... el dolor sigue siendo intenso."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1218
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_fd42d2b0:

    # I "If I knew how to help her..."
    I "Si supiera cómo ayudarla..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1221
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_f99a0b4c:

    # Z "Do you believe this will pass as well? For her?"
    Z "¿Crees que esto también pasará? ¿Para ella?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1224
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_0c0f4d6d:

    # I "I have to."
    I "Tengo que creerlo."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1225
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_e1a6d92b:

    # I "But I can't make that choice for her."
    I "Pero no puedo tomar esa decisión por ella."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1226
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_595c3679:

    # I "I can't stand beside her every moment of every day in case she..."
    I "No puedo estar a su lado cada momento de cada día por si ella..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1227
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_3ab0cadd:

    # "She pauses, not daring to speak it out..."
    "Hace una pausa, sin atreverse a decirlo en voz alta..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1228
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_f97f579b:

    # I "All I can do is stay within reach."
    I "Todo lo que puedo hacer es quedarme a su alcance."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1235
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_feaaf7c5:

    # Z "Do you ever think of leaving this part of the world behind for good?"
    Z "¿Alguna vez piensas en dejar atrás esta parte del mundo para siempre?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1238
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_5018f220_1:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1241
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_7b976c57:

    # I "Yes... More often than you'd think."
    I "Sí... Más a menudo de lo que crees."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1244
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_2f7f5e9f:

    # "She pauses..."
    "Hace una pausa..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1247
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_b46ef0ad:

    # I "I've spent so long walking in one direction that it feels strange not to wonder where the road keeps going."
    I "He pasado tanto tiempo caminando en una dirección que me parece extraño no preguntarme hacia dónde sigue el camino."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1250
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_c5477e48:

    # Z "Yet you're still here."
    Z "Sin embargo, sigues aquí."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1253
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_e55e4958:

    # I "Because this place isn't finished with me."
    I "Porque este lugar no ha terminado conmigo."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1254
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_83d9faf4:

    # I "I see my life as chapters. If I left now and closed this one, I think a part of me would always be looking back."
    I "Veo mi vida como capítulos. Si me fuera ahora y cerrara este, creo que una parte de mí siempre estaría mirando atrás."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1255
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_65ac186a:

    # Z "And your past chapters? They are closed?"
    Z "¿Y tus capítulos pasados? ¿Están cerrados?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1256
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_dc20318c:

    # I "I think so."
    I "Creo que sí."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1257
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_edca8cb1:

    # I "Some I closed myself."
    I "Algunos los cerré yo."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1258
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_d4eb96f0:

    # I "Some were closed for me."
    I "Otros los cerraron por mí."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1259
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_0922059d:

    # "Her gaze drifts somewhere far beyond the walls, beyond the forests, beyond the horizon itself."
    "Su mirada se pierde en algún lugar más allá de los muros, más allá de los bosques, más allá del propio horizonte."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1265
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_ae680c48:

    # Z "You mentioned traveling east before. Where are you really from, [I]? Can you tell me something about your past chapters?"
    Z "Mencionaste viajar al este antes. ¿De dónde eres realmente, [I]? ¿Puedes contarme algo sobre tus capítulos pasados?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1266
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_9483f3b2:

    # "She is quiet for a moment."
    "Permanece en silencio un momento."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1269
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_e184f093:

    # "Then she smiles."
    "Entonces sonríe."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1272
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_bccbab43:

    # I "My mother always told me that memories grow heavier the longer you carry them."
    I "Mi madre siempre me decía que los recuerdos se vuelven más pesados cuanto más tiempo los cargas."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1275
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_c6785427:

    # I "The truth is..."
    I "La verdad es..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1276
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_fe1fc272:

    # I "I don't actually have a memory of the place I am from."
    I "En realidad no tengo ningún recuerdo del lugar del que vengo."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1279
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_8439c1eb:

    # I "I never saw it with my own eyes."
    I "Nunca lo vi con mis propios ojos."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1280
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_0f428204:

    # I "Everything I know from my youngest years came from her retelling."
    I "Todo lo que sé de mis años más jóvenes proviene de sus relatos."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1286
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_8af53728:

    # "You extend your hand..."
    "Extiendes la mano..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1287
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_026a0e6d:

    # Z "Show me."
    Z "Muéstramelo."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1290
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_5018f220_2:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1293
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_5d0c4cce:

    # I "She would picture a slender string of islands, and somewhere in them, a big city. Tall, full of lights, yet grey and endless..."
    I "Ella imaginaba una delgada cadena de islas, y en algún lugar de ellas, una gran ciudad. Alta, llena de luces, pero gris e interminable..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1294
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_4b77effc:

    # I "She remembered the sound of rainfall, the smell of food drifting in from open windows."
    I "Recordaba el sonido de la lluvia, el olor a comida que entraba por las ventanas abiertas."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1295
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_cf99407a:

    # I "People there spent their lives surrounded by countless others. They were connected in every possible way."
    I "La gente de allí pasaba su vida rodeada de innumerables otros. Estaban conectados de todas las formas posibles."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1296
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_3c9826d2:

    # I "But then, the stories changed..."
    I "Pero entonces, las historias cambiaron..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1297
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_02994dd9:

    # I "...they became lonely."
    I "...se volvieron solitarias."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1298
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_25a44810:

    # I "Wandering through life aimlessly, only ever thinking about what's in front of them."
    I "Deambulando por la vida sin rumbo, solo pensando en lo que tienen delante."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1299
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_616fcc41:

    # I "My mother used to say they became so distracted by the noises that they forgot to listen. Or chose not to."
    I "Mi madre solía decir que se distrajeron tanto con los ruidos que se olvidaron de escuchar. O eligieron no hacerlo."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1300
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_22db2da3:

    # I "To each other... and also themselves."
    I "A los demás... y también a sí mismos."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1301
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_79817a76:

    # I "The things that matter... they never disappeared. People just stopped looking for them."
    I "Las cosas que importan... nunca desaparecieron. La gente simplemente dejó de buscarlas."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1306
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_1babd752:

    # I "Maybe one day I'll go back to her..."
    I "Quizá algún día vuelva a su lado..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1307
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_0435264a:

    # I "...and then she will listen to my stories instead."
    I "...y entonces será ella quien escuche mis historias."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1314
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_de1a31e6:

    # Z "I wonder... have you and Sonmi ever been closer than now?"
    Z "Me pregunto... ¿has estado alguna vez más cerca de Sonmi que ahora?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1315
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_40b2acba:

    # Z "Something... more?"
    Z "¿Algo... más?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1318
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_fea67d72:

    # "She blushes..."
    "Se sonroja..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1321
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_9d73ac5a:

    # I "I..."
    I "Yo..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1322
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_ccf3c735:

    # I "I don't think I've ever really looked at girls in that way."
    I "No creo que haya mirado nunca a las chicas de esa manera."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1325
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_2f7f5e9f_1:

    # "She pauses..."
    "Hace una pausa..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1328
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_49e96095:

    # I "And Sonmi..."
    I "Y Sonmi..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1329
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_df9bd20b:

    # I "She's spent so much of her life trying to survive, she never had much chance to think about what she wants to live for."
    I "Ha pasado gran parte de su vida intentando sobrevivir, nunca tuvo muchas oportunidades para pensar en aquello por lo que quiere vivir."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1330
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_5cf24b66:

    # I "I hope she gets the chance one day..."
    I "Espero que algún día tenga la oportunidad..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1331
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_117032c5:

    # I "...to find someone."
    I "...de encontrar a alguien."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1334
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_655f31a6:

    # I "Someone who makes her feel safer than I could."
    I "Alguien que la haga sentir más segura de lo que yo podría."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1335
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_0d62be58:

    # I "Someone who stays, for all the many years she still has ahead of her..."
    I "Alguien que se quede, durante todos los años que aún tiene por delante..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1338
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_09324cbf:

    # "She waits for a moment."
    "Espera un momento."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1341
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_8c9a0f17:

    # I "Perhaps I am like a sister to her."
    I "Quizá soy como una hermana para ella."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1342
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_ed81d487:

    # I "Though..."
    I "Aunque..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1343
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_3eca04f4:

    # I "I could never replace the real one."
    I "Nunca podría reemplazar a la verdadera."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1349
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_e11d8db7:

    # I "She was supposed to be there... Lunai."
    I "Se suponía que ella debía estar ahí... Lunai."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1350
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_7af60108:

    # I "They should have discovered the world together."
    I "Deberían haber descubierto el mundo juntas."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1351
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_74b96b12:

    # I "Still..."
    I "Aún así..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1352
translate spanish d21a_ivy_conversation_9ae8bdd1:

    # I "I think Lunai would be happy to know she isn't alone."
    I "Creo que Lunai se alegraría de saber que no está sola."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1360
translate spanish d21a172_a7127352:

    # I "Now that I think of it... I don't remember the last time I talked about myself that much."
    I "Ahora que lo pienso... no recuerdo la última vez que hablé tanto de mí misma."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1363
translate spanish d21a172_ddb03c6f:

    # "You pause, caught off guard..."
    "Haces una pausa, desprevenido..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1364
translate spanish d21a172_900f0148:

    # Z "Hm..."
    Z "Hm..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1367
translate spanish d21a172_7dab479d:

    # Z "Being able to isn't such a bad thing, right?"
    Z "Poder hacerlo no es algo malo, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1372
translate spanish d21a172_b03f8463:

    # I "It is not a bad feeling, no. I like it a lot."
    I "No es una sensación mala, no. Me gusta mucho."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1373
translate spanish d21a172_258160be:

    # "Her head rests on your shoulder as your gaze follows the subtle movement of the water below you..."
    "Su cabeza descansa sobre tu hombro mientras tu mirada sigue el sutil movimiento del agua bajo vosotros..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1376
translate spanish d21a172_5018f220:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1379
translate spanish d21a172_0044e56f:

    # Z "Is something on your mind?"
    Z "¿Tienes algo en mente?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1385
translate spanish d21a172_51912d26:

    # I "Was I that obvious?"
    I "¿Era tan evidente?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1388
translate spanish d21a172_37a8f4e8:

    # Z "A little."
    Z "Un poco."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1391
translate spanish d21a172_594db3ee:

    # I "It's just..."
    I "Es solo que..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1392
translate spanish d21a172_c9d163b2:

    # I "You know much about me now..."
    I "Ahora sabes mucho de mí..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1393
translate spanish d21a172_99aca996:

    # I "But I still feel like there are parts of you I don't know."
    I "Pero todavía siento que hay partes de ti que no conozco."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1396
translate spanish d21a172_ce27d47f:

    # Z "Hm."
    Z "Hm."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1399
translate spanish d21a172_000250cb:

    # I "I don't mean your title, or the fact that you seem to be who everyone comes to when they need something."
    I "No me refiero a tu título, ni al hecho de que parezcas ser a quien todos acuden cuando necesitan algo."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1400
translate spanish d21a172_1be51a2c:

    # "She searches for the words."
    "Busca las palabras."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1403
translate spanish d21a172_5b82d305:

    # I "The person before who you are now."
    I "La persona anterior a quien eres ahora."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1404
translate spanish d21a172_5b2a1dd4:

    # I "What kind of life did you imagine for yourself?"
    I "¿Qué tipo de vida imaginabas para ti?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1405
translate spanish d21a172_900f0148_1:

    # Z "Hm..."
    Z "Hm..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1406
translate spanish d21a172_ff084423:

    # Z "That's a big question."
    Z "Esa es una gran pregunta."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1408
translate spanish d21a172_a9d1b830:

    # I "You don't have to answer."
    I "No tienes que responder."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1409
translate spanish d21a172_1ccdd58d:

    # Z "No, it's fair."
    Z "No, es justo."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1415
translate spanish d21a172_8c9831c3:

    # Z "I wanted to become the kind of fighter people listened to."
    Z "Quería convertirme en el tipo de guerrero al que la gente escuchara."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1416
translate spanish d21a172_6310386d:

    # Z "I learned early on that strength mattered."
    Z "Aprendí muy pronto que la fuerza importaba."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1417
translate spanish d21a172_4ea03efb:

    # Z "People listen to strong men. Respect and trust them."
    Z "La gente escucha a los hombres fuertes. Los respetan y confían en ellos."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1418
translate spanish d21a172_a56f25f9:

    # Z "That's what I wanted. And once I stared earning it..."
    Z "Eso es lo que quería. Y una vez que empecé a ganármelo..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1419
translate spanish d21a172_dfb8c37d:

    # Z "I discovered I rather enjoyed having a say and a hand in how things turned out."
    Z "Descubrí que disfrutaba bastante teniendo voz y voto en cómo resultaban las cosas."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1420
translate spanish d21a172_b8da30b7:

    # Z "Having standing amongst powerful people. Having influence on their decisions and in turn being useful to them."
    Z "Tener posición entre personas poderosas. Tener influencia en sus decisiones y, a cambio, serles útil."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1425
translate spanish d21a172_debeb5c9:

    # Z "I needed to feel that my life was contributing to something larger than myself."
    Z "Necesitaba sentir que mi vida contribuía a algo más grande que yo."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1426
translate spanish d21a172_a84ed700:

    # Z "I've spent enough time beyond the city walls to understand how fortunate we are."
    Z "He pasado suficiente tiempo fuera de las murallas para entender lo afortunados que somos."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1427
translate spanish d21a172_1fca9078:

    # Z "Zeta isn't perfect, but compared to what's out there..."
    Z "Zeta no es perfecta, pero comparada con lo que hay ahí fuera..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1429
translate spanish d21a172_7024ebe1:

    # Z "Everything I've done... It has never really been about me."
    Z "Todo lo que he hecho... nunca ha sido realmente sobre mí."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1430
translate spanish d21a172_71756a42:

    # Z "People died building what we have. Sacrificed their lives in ways most people couldn't possibly understand."
    Z "Gente murió construyendo lo que tenemos. Sacrificaron sus vidas de formas que la mayoría de la gente no podría entender."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1431
translate spanish d21a172_147283a9:

    # Z "I want to continue that."
    Z "Quiero continuar con eso."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1432
translate spanish d21a172_a352855c:

    # Z "Help build a better place. One worth living in."
    Z "Ayudar a construir un lugar mejor. Uno en el que merezca la pena vivir."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1438
translate spanish d21a172_47688809:

    # Z "I always wanted to come back to a full house."
    Z "Siempre quise volver a una casa llena."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1439
translate spanish d21a172_73cb6a99:

    # Z "I spend a lot of life travelling. Most of it alone."
    Z "Paso gran parte de mi vida viajando. La mayor parte del tiempo solo."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1440
translate spanish d21a172_e6b2ac11:

    # Z "Sometimes a few days. Sometimes weeks."
    Z "A veces unos días. A veces semanas."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1441
translate spanish d21a172_2975c1d1:

    # Z "After a while, you start noticing the difference between arriving somewhere..."
    Z "Al cabo de un tiempo, empiezas a notar la diferencia entre llegar a algún sitio..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1442
translate spanish d21a172_ba13a3e3:

    # Z "And coming home."
    Z "Y volver a casa."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1443
translate spanish d21a172_d0baa70f:

    # Z "That's what I've always wanted."
    Z "Eso es lo que siempre he querido."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1444
translate spanish d21a172_be96af7f:

    # Z "Coming home to a house full of life. Someone to share it with..."
    Z "Volver a casa, a una casa llena de vida. Alguien con quien compartirla..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1445
translate spanish d21a172_bbe9b3a2:

    # Z "A woman. Safety. Stability. A household you can call your own."
    Z "Una mujer. Seguridad. Estabilidad. Un hogar al que puedas llamar tuyo."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1446
translate spanish d21a172_9027f757:

    # Z "The sort of things you don't appreciate until you've spent enough nights sleeping alone."
    Z "El tipo de cosas que no aprecias hasta que has pasado suficientes noches durmiendo solo."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1447
translate spanish d21a172_7f35e3f0:

    # Z "That's what I have worked towards and I can say with some pride that it is largely what I obtained."
    Z "Eso es por lo que he trabajado y puedo decir con cierto orgullo que es en gran parte lo que he obtenido."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1453
translate spanish d21a172_a04b2117:

    # Z "I always wanted to see more of the world."
    Z "Siempre quise ver más mundo."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1454
translate spanish d21a172_b6a57133:

    # Z "I've travelled for as long as I can remember."
    Z "He viajado desde que tengo memoria."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1455
translate spanish d21a172_b3271935:

    # Z "I've spent most of my life chasing distant places, and somehow never managed to leave this corner of the world."
    Z "He pasado la mayor parte de mi vida persiguiendo lugares lejanos, y de alguna manera nunca logré salir de este rincón del mundo."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1456
translate spanish d21a172_7da528fb:

    # Z "I've seen more of the old kingdom than most people ever will."
    Z "He visto más del viejo reino que la mayoría de la gente jamás verá."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1457
translate spanish d21a172_7c9ac0bd:

    # Z "But there is still an entire world out there."
    Z "Pero aún hay un mundo entero ahí fuera."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1458
translate spanish d21a172_688645cd:

    # Z "I still want to see it. Even now that my pace is steadier and my heart is with my family."
    Z "Todavía quiero verlo. Incluso ahora que mi ritmo es más pausado y mi corazón está con mi familia."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1465
translate spanish d21a_romance_menu_20ec5275:

    # "You pause, feeling her head rest on your shoulder, listening quietly..."
    "Haces una pausa, sintiendo su cabeza descansar en tu hombro, escuchando en silencio..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1471
translate spanish d21a_romance_442a578e:

    # "You wrap your arm around her..."
    "Rodeas su cintura con el brazo..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1474
translate spanish d21a_romance_c4854506:

    # "...and pull her in, just a little closer."
    "...y la atraes hacia ti, un poco más cerca."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1477
translate spanish d21a_romance_0c881a20:

    # "Surprised, she looks over to you..."
    "Sorprendida, te mira..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1483
translate spanish d21a_romance_5018f220:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1500
translate spanish d21a_ivy_response_61d26b28:

    # I "Everywhere I've been, it's always the same."
    I "Todos los lugares donde he estado, es siempre igual."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1501
translate spanish d21a_ivy_response_0743c6f5:

    # I "The things people value may change..."
    I "Las cosas que la gente valora pueden cambiar..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1502
translate spanish d21a_ivy_response_3bdd2192:

    # I "But everyone needs something that earns them a place in the world."
    I "Pero todos necesitan algo que les gane un lugar en el mundo."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1506
translate spanish d21a_ivy_response_c19ac202:

    # "She smiles..."
    "Sonríe..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1513
translate spanish d21a_ivy_response_ffc6a0f7:

    # I "You know... I think there is something you missed."
    I "¿Sabes?... Creo que hay algo que pasaste por alto."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1517
translate spanish d21a_ivy_response_3d9b57ea:

    # Z "Hm?"
    Z "¿Hm?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1518
translate spanish d21a_ivy_response_fae575e4:

    # I "You talked about strength. About wanting people to listen to you."
    I "Hablaste de la fuerza. De querer que la gente te escuche."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1519
translate spanish d21a_ivy_response_21139404:

    # I "But I don't think that's why they do."
    I "Pero no creo que sea por eso que lo hacen."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1520
translate spanish d21a_ivy_response_2f500df0:

    # Z "No?"
    Z "¿No?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1521
translate spanish d21a_ivy_response_cc2853e3:

    # I "People listen to you because you make them feel safe."
    I "La gente te escucha porque les haces sentir seguros."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1522
translate spanish d21a_ivy_response_b171a555:

    # I "I noticed that the day you brought me to your home."
    I "Me di cuenta el día que me llevaste a tu casa."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1526
translate spanish d21a_ivy_response_4b0632dd:

    # "She leans on you more..."
    "Se apoya más en ti..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1527
translate spanish d21a_ivy_response_04da1a82:

    # I "It's rare, in these times..."
    I "Es raro, en estos tiempos..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1531
translate spanish d21a_ivy_response_e4584273:

    # I "...to feel safe around someone."
    I "...sentirse segura junto a alguien."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1535
translate spanish d21a_ivy_response_11c92675:

    # I "It's a noble cause..."
    I "Es una causa noble..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1536
translate spanish d21a_ivy_response_d05dafdf:

    # I "I can imagine Zeta being a lovely place to settle down in."
    I "Puedo imaginar Zeta como un lugar encantador para establecerse."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1537
translate spanish d21a_ivy_response_b05fb244:

    # I "...For those who are allowed to call it home and have the means for it, that is."
    I "...Para aquellos que pueden llamarlo hogar y tienen los medios para ello, claro."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1544
translate spanish d21a_ivy_response_847572c3:

    # "She leans in closer to your shoulder..."
    "Se acerca más a tu hombro..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1548
translate spanish d21a_ivy_response_3695b9f5:

    # I "I hope you succeed."
    I "Espero que lo consigas."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1552
translate spanish d21a_ivy_response_921b140b:

    # I "You know..."
    I "¿Sabes?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1553
translate spanish d21a_ivy_response_81987b1a:

    # I "So far, I have only briefly seen it from the inside."
    I "Hasta ahora, solo lo he visto brevemente desde dentro."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1557
translate spanish d21a_ivy_response_7aa67518:

    # I "When you talk about it like that, I can almost believe it..."
    I "Cuando hablas de ello así, casi puedo creerlo..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1561
translate spanish d21a_ivy_response_a5e1b94f:

    # I "...that it could be nice to live in such a place."
    I "...que podría ser agradable vivir en un lugar así."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1564
translate spanish d21a_ivy_response_7324921d:

    # I "I understand."
    I "Lo entiendo."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1565
translate spanish d21a_ivy_response_81d28a31:

    # I "I don't think I've ever had that..."
    I "No creo que haya tenido eso nunca..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1566
translate spanish d21a_ivy_response_bbfcd2ac:

    # I "Someone to return home to. Someone waiting for me..."
    I "Alguien a quien volver. Alguien esperándome..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1576
translate spanish d21a_ivy_response_387c0104:

    # I "Not even with Sonmi's people."
    I "Ni siquiera con la gente de Sonmi."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1580
translate spanish d21a_ivy_response_9049dc6e:

    # I "It sounds nice. Sweet, even."
    I "Suena bien. Dulce, incluso."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1581
translate spanish d21a_ivy_response_226ed3ae:

    # I "I can see why you would want that."
    I "Puedo ver por qué querrías eso."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1582
translate spanish d21a_ivy_response_86fd004c:

    # I "I've travelled for so long that I never really stopped to imagine what it might feel like."
    I "He viajado tanto tiempo que nunca me detuve a imaginar cómo podría sentirse."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1583
translate spanish d21a_ivy_response_c75578b2:

    # I "Coming home to someone."
    I "Volver a casa con alguien."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1587
translate spanish d21a_ivy_response_139add94:

    # "She thinks for a moment..."
    "Piensa un momento..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1588
translate spanish d21a_ivy_response_341c4be8:

    # I "Perhaps I've simply never had the opportunity."
    I "Quizá simplemente nunca tuve la oportunidad."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1592
translate spanish d21a_ivy_response_7daacfa4:

    # I "It sounds like something I could learn to like..."
    I "Suena a algo que podría aprender a querer..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1595
translate spanish d21a_ivy_response_7f5842d8:

    # I "You strike me as someone who belongs on the road."
    I "Me pareces alguien que pertenece al camino."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1606
translate spanish d21a_ivy_response_e409965d:

    # I "Perhaps one day you'll finally leave the desert..."
    I "Quizá algún día finalmente dejes el desierto..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1610
translate spanish d21a_ivy_response_9cdf2e6a:

    # I "And find out what lies beyond."
    I "Y descubras lo que hay más allá."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1611
translate spanish d21a_ivy_response_6ac0a031:

    # I "The strange thing is..."
    I "Lo extraño es..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1612
translate spanish d21a_ivy_response_a2b11f70:

    # I "No matter how much of the world you see, there's always another, more different road."
    I "No importa cuánto mundo veas, siempre hay otro camino, más diferente."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1616
translate spanish d21a_ivy_response_cc016d58:

    # I "I think you'd like that."
    I "Creo que te gustaría eso."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1620
translate spanish d21a_ivy_response_8673a337:

    # I "Maybe one day, your curiosity will get the better of you, after all?"
    I "Quizá algún día, tu curiosidad termine por vencerte, ¿no crees?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1634
translate spanish d21a208_b83147fe:

    # "Her eyes meet yours..."
    "Sus ojos se encuentran con los tuyos..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1637
translate spanish d21a208_5018f220:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1644
translate spanish d21a208_8e5bf2eb:

    # "...and neither of you look away."
    "...y ninguno de los dos aparta la mirada."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1647
translate spanish d21a208_5018f220_1:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1650
translate spanish d21a208_47b02d24:

    # "You place your hand under her cheek..."
    "Pones la mano bajo su mejilla..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1653
translate spanish d21a208_99b4e8f2:

    # "...and caress it gently, feeling her soft skin."
    "...y la acaricias suavemente, sintiendo su piel suave."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1656
translate spanish d21a208_717ffdb9:

    # "You look into her pink eyes, lost in the moment. She does not look surprised anymore."
    "Miras sus ojos rosados, perdido en el momento. Ya no parece sorprendida."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1659
translate spanish d21a208_5ea9b7db:

    # "...and then, just a moment later..."
    "...y entonces, solo un momento después..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1662
translate spanish d21a208_214d0673:

    # "...all but one of your thoughts fade away."
    "...todos tus pensamientos, excepto uno, se desvanecen."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1665
translate spanish d21a208_b51f8ba3:

    # "You kiss..."
    "La besas..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1666
translate spanish d21a208_eb35ad2f:

    # I "Mh..."
    I "Mh..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1669
translate spanish d21a208_61572a7e:

    # "You don't notice her nervously clenched fist relaxing as her lips join yours."
    "No notas cómo su puño, nerviosamente apretado, se relaja cuando sus labios se unen a los tuyos."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1670
translate spanish d21a208_86a67345:

    # I "{i}*kissing*{/i}"
    I "{i}*besándose*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1671
translate spanish d21a208_5cad4bca:

    # "You hold her tight, and she gives in to you, in a moment you did not expect, but quietly hoped for."
    "La abrazas fuerte, y ella se entrega a ti, en un momento que no esperabas, pero que deseabas en silencio."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1672
translate spanish d21a208_b056fa64:

    # "Perhaps... she did too?"
    "Quizá... ¿ella también?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1675
translate spanish d21a208_1c87bb40:

    # "Your thumb scours the edge of her cheekbone, a gentle caress as your breaths combine."
    "Tu pulgar recorre el borde de su pómulo, una caricia suave mientras vuestras respiraciones se combinan."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1678
translate spanish d21a208_5f06b882:

    # "A quiet, hushed, murmur escapes her as you capture her upper lip."
    "Un murmullo callado, apenas un susurro, escapa de ella mientras atrapas su labio superior."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1681
translate spanish d21a208_832bc9ac:

    # "She follows suit, almost playfully..."
    "Ella te imita, casi con picardía..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1684
translate spanish d21a208_bf2cbd32:

    # "For several minutes, everything around you falls silent."
    "Durante varios minutos, todo a tu alrededor se queda en silencio."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1685
translate spanish d21a208_4a487d4d:

    # "And all that can be heard is the intimate exchange of tenderness."
    "Y todo lo que se oye es el íntimo intercambio de ternura."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1693
translate spanish d21a208_851ef47e:

    # "You lean back, still mesmerized by her softness and taste..."
    "Te reclinas, todavía hechizado por su suavidad y su sabor..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1696
translate spanish d21a208_14caf688:

    # "...and see her eyes wander away from you."
    "...y ves cómo sus ojos se alejan de los tuyos."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1699
translate spanish d21a208_6b3c6d48:

    # "And then, she quickly stands up..."
    "Y entonces, se levanta rápidamente..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1702
translate spanish d21a208_9fb60066:

    # I "You... have a wife, [persistent.player_name]."
    I "Tú... tienes esposa, [persistent.player_name]."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1705
translate spanish d21a208_c5c3cf7f:

    # I "I have lived long enough to know what this is."
    I "He vivido lo suficiente para saber lo que es esto."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1708
translate spanish d21a208_fee9a906:

    # "You think about her words and what they mean..."
    "Piensas en sus palabras y en lo que significan..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1711
translate spanish d21a208_baaf921c:

    # "...and then approach her."
    "...y luego te acercas a ella."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1714
translate spanish d21a208_d5f681c0:

    # Z "You are afraid of coming between something..."
    Z "Temes interponerte entre algo..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1715
translate spanish d21a208_5018f220_2:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1718
translate spanish d21a208_4b155f80:

    # "You close up on her..."
    "Te acercas a ella..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1721
translate spanish d21a208_10a063bb:

    # Z "Look at me..."
    Z "Mírame..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1724
translate spanish d21a208_ba699ad2:

    # Z "You are a kind soul, [I]."
    Z "Eres un alma bondadosa, [I]."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1727
translate spanish d21a208_5018f220_3:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1728
translate spanish d21a208_a0ff5ab2:

    # Z "But you worry too much."
    Z "Pero te preocupas demasiado."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1731
translate spanish d21a208_2c263250:

    # "You let go of her cheek..."
    "Sueltas su mejilla..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1734
translate spanish d21a208_06664188:

    # "...and admire her blue eyes, trying to understand their meaning."
    "… y admiras sus ojos azules, tratando de entender su significado."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1737
translate spanish d21a208_8887e0ce:

    # Z "I will travel back home, now."
    Z "Volveré a casa, ahora."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1740
translate spanish d21a208_5018f220_4:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1741
translate spanish d21a208_f340e0a5:

    # "Her smile fades in surprise..."
    "Su sonrisa se desvanece con sorpresa..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1746
translate spanish d21a219_0a12c2a4:

    # I "Can you..."
    I "¿Puedes..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1747
translate spanish d21a219_4501d7bc:

    # I "...come back and see me again?"
    I "...volver y verme de nuevo?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1750
translate spanish d21a219_a567f736:

    # Z "I will, [I]. Soon."
    Z "Lo haré, [I]. Pronto."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1756
translate spanish d21a219_dc17f809:

    # "After a while, you realize it is getting late, and so you both stand up and prepare to say bye."
    "Al cabo de un rato, te das cuenta de que se está haciendo tarde, así que ambos se levantan y se preparan para despedirse."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1759
translate spanish d21a219_c3b51781:

    # I "You are always invited to visit again, [persistent.player_name]."
    I "Siempre estás invitado a visitarnos de nuevo, [persistent.player_name]."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1762
translate spanish d21a219_8fd0cf97:

    # Z "Thank you, [I]. And yes, I will return soon."
    Z "Gracias, [I]. Y sí, volveré pronto."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1763
translate spanish d21a219_0775e184:

    # Z "I need to know if she comes back."
    Z "Necesito saber si ella vuelve."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1778
translate spanish d21a219_f0fa05c1:

    # "Eventually, you make your way home, telling yourself to return again soon."
    "Finalmente, emprendes el camino a casa, diciéndote a ti mismo que vuelvas pronto."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1785
translate spanish d21b_a8f208f5:

    # Zt "It has been a few days since Sonmi disappeared again."
    Zt "Han pasado unos días desde que Sonmi desapareció de nuevo."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1786
translate spanish d21b_5026fd25:

    # Zt "Tonight, I will go to their hideout and see how [I] is doing."
    Zt "Esta noche, iré a su escondite para ver cómo está [I]."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1790
translate spanish d21b_a8856104:

    # "You start your car after the sun sets, travelling under the cover of darkness, to preserve the secret of their location."
    "Arrancas el coche después del atardecer, viajando al amparo de la oscuridad, para preservar el secreto de su ubicación."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1802
translate spanish d21b_5f995ffb:

    # "While searching for [I], you find familiar blue plants towering over the area where you last saw her friend..."
    "Mientras buscas a [I], encuentras plantas azules familiares elevándose sobre la zona donde viste a su amiga por última vez..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1803
translate spanish d21b_bd79084b:

    # Zt "I remember these... but how could they grow here so quickly?"
    Zt "Recuerdo estas... ¿pero cómo pudieron crecer tan rápido aquí?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1806
translate spanish d21b_92a6ee76:

    # "Focused on studying the plants, you overhear gentle footsteps behind you..."
    "Centrado en estudiar las plantas, oyes pasos suaves detrás de ti..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1812
translate spanish d21b_5018f220:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1821
translate spanish d21b_5018f220_1:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1824
translate spanish d21b_3d9c096f:

    # I "They are fast climbing organisms, aren't they? Sometimes, you can even watch them grow in real time."
    I "Son organismos de crecimiento rápido, ¿verdad? A veces, incluso puedes verlos crecer en tiempo real."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1827
translate spanish d21b_8e158df7:

    # Z "I was just here a few days ago. This place... it completely changed."
    Z "Estuve aquí hace solo unos días. Este lugar... ha cambiado por completo."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1830
translate spanish d21b_a1e814e5:

    # I "The quicker things change, the more unnatural they seem to us."
    I "Cuanto más rápido cambian las cosas, más antinaturales nos parecen."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1831
translate spanish d21b_14795e5c:

    # I "And yet, even the most unnatural things, when touched by life, want only to grow. Life finds a way."
    I "Y sin embargo, incluso las cosas más antinaturales, cuando son tocadas por la vida, solo quieren crecer. La vida encuentra un camino."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1838
translate spanish d21b_5018f220_2:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1841
translate spanish d21b_8d2d5205:

    # I "Sonmi has not returned."
    I "Sonmi no ha vuelto."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1848
translate spanish d21b_171c11c0:

    # Z "Oh, I see..."
    Z "Oh, ya veo..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1851
translate spanish d21b_e593155b:

    # I "I am sorry, [persistent.player_name]. You have come here all the way to see what happened."
    I "Lo siento, [persistent.player_name]. Has venido hasta aquí para ver qué pasaba."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1854
translate spanish d21b_f24d067c:

    # I "If you want, you can spend the night here [persistent.player_name]. It will be safer to return tomorrow."
    I "Si quieres, puedes pasar la noche aquí, [persistent.player_name]. Será más seguro volver mañana."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1857
translate spanish d21b_268f0f01:

    # Z "Perhaps you are right, there is no need to start going back at this hour."
    Z "Quizá tengas razón, no hace falta volver a estas horas."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1858
translate spanish d21b_08d14bc9:

    # Z "I might as well stay the night here. Thank you."
    Z "Mejor me quedo a pasar la noche aquí. Gracias."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1861
translate spanish d21b_54f2351b:

    # I "Are you feeling sleepy, yet? Because I could still use some help with the plants..."
    I "¿Tienes sueño ya? Porque todavía podría usar algo de ayuda con las plantas..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1864
translate spanish d21b_fd8cbb84:

    # Z "Lead the way, [I]."
    Z "Guía el camino, [I]."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1867
translate spanish d21b_c19ac202:

    # "She smiles..."
    "Sonríe..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1872
translate spanish d21b_44daa3ee:

    # Z "I have brought you something."
    Z "Te he traído algo."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1875
translate spanish d21b_0cf06034:

    # I "...?"
    I "¿...?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1876
translate spanish d21b_f56a41b5:

    # Z "Something from our last conversation, about your mother's tales..."
    Z "Algo de nuestra última conversación, sobre los relatos de tu madre..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1877
translate spanish d21b_c2bb41ca:

    # Z "I was thinking about it, your mention of slender islands."
    Z "Estuve pensando en ello, en tu mención de las islas alargadas."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1880
translate spanish d21b_e6e8d1a7:

    # Z "...and went looking through the relics and trinkets I found in my early days."
    Z "...y busqué entre las reliquias y baratijas que encontré en mis primeros años."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1883
translate spanish d21b_ae6518b6:

    # Z "I remembered I once found a map of one such place."
    Z "Recordé que una vez encontré un mapa de uno de esos lugares."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1884
translate spanish d21b_748ad94c:

    # Z "I found this, together with it."
    Z "Encontré esto, junto con él."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1887
translate spanish d21b_22aa2540:

    # Z "I want you to have it."
    Z "Quiero que lo tengas."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1888
translate spanish d21b_d003a97e:

    # I "{i}*gasps*{/i}"
    I "{i}*jadea*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1891
translate spanish d21b_9d73ac5a:

    # I "I..."
    I "Yo..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1894
translate spanish d21b_4f3b4579:

    # I "... yes, I remember this symbol, I think."
    I "... sí, creo que recuerdo este símbolo."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1899
translate spanish d21b_674ae787:

    # Z "Over the years, I have tried to research its meaning..."
    Z "A lo largo de los años, he intentado investigar su significado..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1900
translate spanish d21b_75227977:

    # Z "...but now I believe, it's better left in your hands."
    Z "...pero ahora creo que es mejor que quede en tus manos."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1903
translate spanish d21b_b2967f0a:

    # "You give her the necklace..."
    "Le das el collar..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1906
translate spanish d21b_abc14aa2:

    # I "It is... beautiful."
    I "Es... precioso."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1907
translate spanish d21b_89760357:

    # I "There is a word I read in an old book, many years ago: anemoia. It translates as nostalgia for a place you have never been..."
    I "Hay una palabra que leí en un libro antiguo, hace muchos años: anemoia. Se traduce como nostalgia por un lugar en el que nunca has estado..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1910
translate spanish d21b_6384be0b:

    # I "...but I could not really grasp the concept, until now. I think this might be such a thing."
    I "...pero no podía comprender realmente el concepto, hasta ahora. Creo que esto podría ser una de esas cosas."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1911
translate spanish d21b_3c9a908b:

    # I "Thank you... I will cherish it."
    I "Gracias... lo atesoraré."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1914
translate spanish d21b_24de7138:

    # Z "Do you want to wear it?"
    Z "¿Quieres ponértelo?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1917
translate spanish d21b_f91cc0fe:

    # I "Wear it..."
    I "Ponérmelo..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1920
translate spanish d21b_d38063f8:

    # I "I... don't think I can, or should..."
    I "No... creo que pueda, o deba..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1923
translate spanish d21b_aa308b89:

    # I "It's shiny and fragile, and might get lost. I think I should keep it somewhere safe instead."
    I "Es brillante y frágil, y podría perderse. Creo que debería guardarlo en un lugar seguro."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1926
translate spanish d21b_0e759100:

    # Z "I see. Maybe another time, then."
    Z "Ya veo. Quizá en otro momento, entonces."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1929
translate spanish d21b_0d0f07c3:

    # I "Maybe...!"
    I "¡Quizá...!"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1930
translate spanish d21b_3f1fd1f3:

    # "Her eyes suddenly light up as she realizes something..."
    "Sus ojos se iluminan de repente al darse cuenta de algo..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1933
translate spanish d21b_ee4a5f77:

    # I "I just realized... that I have something from a long time ago."
    I "Acabo de darme cuenta... de que tengo algo de hace mucho tiempo."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1936
translate spanish d21b_1b24edc5:

    # I "Do you mind if I wear this with something else?"
    I "¿Te importa si lo uso con otra cosa?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1939
translate spanish d21b_adba992b:

    # Z "Not at all. Now you've got me curious."
    Z "En absoluto. Ahora me has picado la curiosidad."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1942
translate spanish d21b_ab29f950:

    # I "Okay, I will be back!"
    I "¡Vale, vuelvo enseguida!"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1943
translate spanish d21b_15f8eeec:

    # "She walks back inside, a hurried excitement in her steps..."
    "Vuelve a entrar, con una emoción apresurada en sus pasos..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1948
translate spanish d21b_ef3e728f:

    # Z "Something from a long time ago, hm..."
    Z "Algo de hace mucho tiempo, hm..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1949
translate spanish d21b_60795bab:

    # Z "I wonder what that will be."
    Z "Me pregunto qué será."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1953
translate spanish red21b41_1a8f81c7:

    # "Many minutes pass in silence under the cloudy sky, as you stand on the ancient stones above the water."
    "Pasan muchos minutos en silencio bajo el cielo nublado, mientras estás sobre las antiguas piedras sobre el agua."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1954
translate spanish red21b41_9befd5a2:

    # "And then, as if initiated by the gods themselves..."
    "Y entonces, como si lo hubieran iniciado los propios dioses..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1961
translate spanish red21b41_7db9272e:

    # Zt "...rain?"
    Zt "...¿lluvia?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1964
translate spanish red21b41_fc63bb5f:

    # "a torrential downpour surprises you. Its droplets are warm, pleasant, and surprisingly clean."
    "un aguacero torrencial te sorprende. Sus gotas son cálidas, agradables y sorprendentemente limpias."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1967
translate spanish red21b41_298ac4e5:

    # "...and a slender figure slowly starts to emerge from the inside of the ruins."
    "...y una figura esbelta comienza a emerger lentamente desde el interior de las ruinas."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1970
translate spanish red21b41_a135af23:

    # "She glides smoothly to a halt at the entrance, just out of reach of the rain..."
    "Se desliza suavemente hasta detenerse en la entrada, justo fuera del alcance de la lluvia..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1973
translate spanish red21b41_5018f220:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1976
translate spanish red21b41_e92dfc27:

    # "...and smiles."
    "...y sonríe."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1979
translate spanish red21b41_ba147906:

    # "As she steps into the moonlight, you see a thin veil of fabric that hugs her figure accentuating her curves."
    "Al entrar en la luz de la luna, ves un fino velo de tela que abraza su figura acentuando sus curvas."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1983
translate spanish red21b41_c70145c9:

    # Zt "She looks beautiful."
    Zt "Está preciosa."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1986
translate spanish red21b41_e0443c01:

    # "She steps towards you, into the rain..."
    "Da un paso hacia ti, bajo la lluvia..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1989
translate spanish red21b41_d6ee957d:

    # "...ever closer, the fabric, in places, sticking to her wet skin."
    "...cada vez más cerca, la tela, en algunos lugares, pegada a su piel mojada."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1992
translate spanish red21b41_4279c9a3:

    # "She stands before you: the night dress and the necklace complementing each other, further enhancing her beautiful frame."
    "Se alza ante ti: el vestido de noche y el collar se complementan, realzando aún más su hermoso cuerpo."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1993
translate spanish red21b41_edd44b44:

    # "Gentle eyes, covered by her raven, wet hair, look deep into yours and you respond with open admiration."
    "Ojos suaves, cubiertos por su cabello mojado y negro como el cuervo, miran profundamente los tuyos y respondes con abierta admiración."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1996
translate spanish red21b41_4ef306df:

    # I "I... have not looked at this dress ever since I discovered it."
    I "Yo... no he mirado este vestido desde que lo descubrí."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:1999
translate spanish red21b41_e976ea58:

    # "She pauses, unsure of what to say. Unsure of... how to behave?"
    "Se detiene, insegura de qué decir. Insegura de... ¿cómo comportarse?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:2002
translate spanish red21b41_02660e0d:

    # "You reach out for her..."
    "Extiendes la mano hacia ella..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:2003
translate spanish red21b41_8734c52a:

    # Z "Take my hand."
    Z "Coge mi mano."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:2009
translate spanish red21b41_5018f220_1:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:2012
translate spanish red21b41_92bba03a:

    # "She lays her hand onto yours..."
    "Posa su mano sobre la tuya..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:2015
translate spanish red21b41_6282f14a:

    # "...and you pull her towards you."
    "...y la atraes hacia ti."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:2018
translate spanish red21b41_aeb7c13a:

    # "You take your time holding her in your arms, and start to move... a silent embrace that melts into the merest hint to a dance in the rain."
    "Te tomas tu tiempo para tenerla en brazos, y empiezas a moverte... un abrazo silencioso que se funde en el más leve indicio de un baile bajo la lluvia."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:2019
translate spanish red21b41_aa66cf09:

    # "Minutes pass as she looks at you. Her gentle, pink eyes expressing the timid joy for a moment of shared beauty and closeness..."
    "Pasan los minutos mientras ella te mira. Sus suaves ojos rosados expresan la tímida alegría por un momento de belleza e intimidad compartidas..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:2022
translate spanish red21b41_c2cf1f0c:

    # "...in her characteristic silence, you both find a message..."
    "...en su característico silencio, ambos encontráis un mensaje..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:2023
translate spanish red21b41_48b3879c:

    # "...a mutual invitation to leave this moment with only the weight of the rain, bearing down on your shoulders, refreshed, renewed."
    "...una invitación mutua a dejar este momento con solo el peso de la lluvia, sobre vuestros hombros, renovados, revitalizados."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:2026
translate spanish red21b41_a23c0f9f:

    # "And then, as quickly as it came..."
    "Y entonces, tan rápido como llegó..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:2029
translate spanish red21b41_3144e07b:

    # "...the cloud breaks right above you, leaving you untouched."
    "...la nube se rompe justo encima de vosotros, dejándoos intactos."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:2033
translate spanish red21b41_5018f220_2:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:2038
translate spanish red21b41_32a51cc5:

    # "As you look at [I], her expression shifts, as a million thoughts seem to cross her mind."
    "Al mirar a [I], su expresión cambia, como si un millón de pensamientos cruzaran su mente."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:2039
translate spanish red21b41_d75ffc2c:

    # "She stares at you, her bright eyes shining under the pale light."
    "Te mira fijamente, sus brillantes ojos brillando bajo la pálida luz."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:2040
translate spanish red21b41_22a71bb2:

    # "You look at this woman who straddles the weird dichotomy between looking decades younger than you whilst being decades older."
    "Miras a esta mujer que se sitúa en la extraña dicotomía entre parecer décadas más joven que tú mientras es décadas mayor."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:2041
translate spanish red21b41_ca753af1:

    # "You are left wondering: throughout your interactions with her, you have always sensed in her a curious mixture of world weariness and innocence..."
    "Te quedas preguntándote: a lo largo de tus interacciones con ella, siempre has percibido en ella una curiosa mezcla de cansancio del mundo e inocencia..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:2042
translate spanish red21b41_b32bb0c1:

    # "...and you can't help thinking that maybe, if you were to live as long, you would be a lot more jaded and worn out. "
    "...y no puedes evitar pensar que quizá, si vivieras tanto tiempo, estarías mucho más hastiado y desgastado."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:2043
translate spanish red21b41_5dba808d:

    # "Instead, [I] stands before you and averts her eyes like a young timid girl."
    "En cambio, [I] está ante ti y aparta la mirada como una joven tímida."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:2045
translate spanish red21b41_04f76e8c:

    # "You look at her, your voice firm but gentle..."
    "La miras, con voz firme pero suave..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:2049
translate spanish red21b41_d48ae6aa:

    # Z "...You are beautiful, [I]."
    Z "...Eres hermosa, [I]."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:2052
translate spanish red21b41_49cb3585:

    # I "I...."
    I "Yo..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:2053
translate spanish red21b41_734804d9:

    # I "...don't know what to..."
    I "...no sé qué..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:2057
translate spanish red21b41_325912bc:

    # "And then, under the shining light of the moon, she reaches out for a kiss..."
    "Y entonces, bajo la brillante luz de la luna, ella se inclina para un beso..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:2058
translate spanish red21b41_09aac273:

    # I "mh..."
    I "mh..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:2061
translate spanish red21b41_67da897a:

    # "She reaches for your lips, her arms resting on your shoulders."
    "Busca tus labios, sus brazos descansando sobre tus hombros."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:2062
translate spanish red21b41_5fa31066:

    # "Her kiss is full but nervous. Reserved, and yet eager. Delicate, and yet intoxicating."
    "Su beso es pleno pero nervioso. Reservado, y sin embargo ansioso. Delicado, y sin embargo embriagador."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:2065
translate spanish red21b41_535f31b3:

    # "Minutes pass, as you hold each other, and as you give her the attention she so very much needed."
    "Pasan los minutos, mientras os abrazáis, y mientras le prestas la atención que tanto necesitaba."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:2066
translate spanish red21b41_e7650375:

    # "Tonight is not about duties or responsibilities."
    "Esta noche no se trata de deberes o responsabilidades."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:2067
translate spanish red21b41_88f132ec:

    # "It is not about the countless years where you lived your lives separate from each other, nor about the years she will inevitably spend without you."
