    Z "Vaya..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3794
translate spanish d21b_ivy_lay_eb35ad2f_2:

    # I "Mh..."
    I "Mh..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3797
translate spanish d21b_ivy_lay_a686a842:

    # I "Thank... you..."
    I "Gra... cias..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3800
translate spanish d21b_ivy_lay_5048eb8c:

    # I "mhh..."
    I "mhh..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3801
translate spanish d21b_ivy_lay_04721af9_1:

    # Z "{i}*kissing*{/i}"
    Z "{i}*besándose*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3804
translate spanish d21b_ivy_lay_c52f6088:

    # "Completely spent, she leans against you, moaning quietly, while you kiss and caress her for a minute longer..."
    "Completamente agotada, se apoya contra ti, gimiendo en voz baja, mientras la besas y acaricias un minuto más..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3817
translate spanish d21b401_35703232:

    # "You find yourself in the pond resting against the stone, as the girl you spent the night with swims towards you."
    "Te encuentras en el estanque, descansando contra la piedra, mientras la chica con la que pasaste la noche nada hacia ti."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3820
translate spanish d21b401_5332dbf6:

    # I "Did you know... that for our kind, our ears are the most sensitive in our body?"
    I "¿Sabías... que para nuestra especie, las orejas son lo más sensible de nuestro cuerpo?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3823
translate spanish d21b401_961869bb:

    # Z "I did not, no."
    Z "No, no lo sabía."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3826
translate spanish d21b401_69de9db2:

    # "You gently reach out to her..."
    "Extiendes la mano suavemente hacia ella..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3827
translate spanish d21b401_62c6a949:

    # Z "Tell me then, how exactly does this feel?"
    Z "Dime entonces, ¿cómo se siente exactamente?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3830
translate spanish d21b401_c54f5248:

    # Z "Is it ticklish, or does it hurt?"
    Z "¿Hace cosquillas, o duele?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3831
translate spanish d21b401_360f318a:

    # "You gently rub the back of her pointy ear..."
    "Frotas suavemente la parte trasera de su oreja puntiaguda..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3834
translate spanish d21b401_4bda1bda:

    # I "It's... a unique feeling. It calms me down..."
    I "Es... una sensación única. Me tranquiliza..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3837
translate spanish d21b401_5ccf9c9f:

    # I "...when it's the right person."
    I "...cuando es la persona adecuada."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3840
translate spanish d21b401_65cfa13a:

    # "You look each other into the eyes..."
    "Os miráis a los ojos..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3846
translate spanish d21b401_6e6c3660:

    # "She rests her arms on your shoulder..."
    "Apoya sus brazos sobre tu hombro..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3849
translate spanish d21b401_606a225e:

    # I "And it's an erogenous zone too. It gets us excited."
    I "Y también es una zona erógena. Nos excita."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3852
translate spanish d21b401_d43913fb:

    # Z "Is that so... how excited exactly?"
    Z "¿Ah, sí?... ¿exactamente cómo de excitadas?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3855
translate spanish d21b401_d54caa88:

    # I "Very... it's..."
    I "Mucho... es..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3858
translate spanish d21b401_8714ba2b:

    # I "Ah..."
    I "Ah..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3859
translate spanish d21b401_9202c977:

    # "She lets out a cute moan as she lowers herself on you..."
    "Suelta un gemido adorable mientras se desliza sobre ti..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3860
translate spanish d21b401_bfb981fc:

    # I "...hard to resist."
    I "...difícil de resistir."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3863
translate spanish d21b401_d15cc59a:

    # Z "That's good to know."
    Z "Es bueno saberlo."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3868
translate spanish d21b401_a8b56071:

    # I "Thank you for this very special night, [persistent.player_name]."
    I "Gracias por esta noche tan especial, [persistent.player_name]."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3869
translate spanish d21b401_25575128:

    # I "I... appreciate you taking your time for Sonmi... and me."
    I "Agradezco... que hayas dedicado tiempo a Sonmi... y a mí."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3872
translate spanish d21b401_ac591083:

    # I "It has been such a long time... I forgot how much I could enjoy it."
    I "Ha pasado tanto tiempo... olvidé cuánto podía disfrutarlo."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3875
translate spanish d21b401_389f87f3:

    # I "...and I am not just talking about the physical side."
    I "...y no hablo solo de la parte física."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3880
translate spanish d21b401_143ea5f6:

    # Z "And you deserved it. After everything you went through."
    Z "Y lo merecías. Después de todo lo que has pasado."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3881
translate spanish d21b401_844d8b44:

    # Z "You are a fascinating woman, [I]. I was struck since the moment we met."
    Z "Eres una mujer fascinante, [I]. Me cautivaste desde el momento en que nos conocimos."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3884
translate spanish d21b401_c19ac202:

    # "She smiles..."
    "Sonríe..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3887
translate spanish d21b401_fdecf524:

    # I "Do you mind, if..."
    I "¿Te importa si..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3888
translate spanish d21b401_e41484f6:

    # Z "...we keep going?"
    Z "...seguimos?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3889
translate spanish d21b401_8ae932d8:

    # I "How did you..."
    I "¿Cómo has..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3892
translate spanish d21b401_79ce1ed5:

    # "You hold her firmly..."
    "La sujetas con firmeza..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3893
translate spanish d21b401_6add1b6c:

    # Z "Well... I'd say I'm beginning to understand how \"elves\" really work. Or maybe it's just you I am getting to know."
    Z "Bueno... diría que empiezo a entender cómo funcionan realmente las \"elfas\". O quizá solo te estoy conociendo a ti."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3894
translate spanish d21b401_6b00fc4b:

    # I "{i}*giggles*{/i}"
    I "{i}*risitas*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3897
translate spanish d21b401_daa515c1:

    # I "But just how long can you really last, hm?"
    I "Pero, ¿cuánto puedes aguantar realmente, hm?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3900
translate spanish d21b401_b8f1c3e1:

    # Z "Let's find out, together."
    Z "Descubrámoslo, juntos."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3903
translate spanish d21b401_997a0a98:

    # "And so you kiss again, under the same moonlight that guided you to this place."
    "Y así os besáis de nuevo, bajo la misma luz de luna que os guió hasta este lugar."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3904
translate spanish d21b401_d79346ab:

    # "The elf who already taught you so much about yourself since the moment you saved her..."
    "La elfa que ya te ha enseñado tanto sobre ti mismo desde el momento en que la salvaste..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3905
translate spanish d21b401_39d3f56a:

    # "...still seems to have a few more lessons for you prepared."
    "...parece que aún tiene preparadas algunas lecciones más para ti."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3909
translate spanish d21b401_c6c81b3a:

    # "Before you know it, you both fall asleep together, and what seems to be a long, dreamy night, comes to an end."
    "Antes de que te des cuenta, ambos os quedáis dormidos juntos, y lo que parece una larga y soñadora noche, llega a su fin."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3913
translate spanish d21b401_48555229:

    # "She smiles, but behind her sweet facade, hides a lifetime of loneliness..."
    "Sonríe, pero detrás de su dulce fachada, se esconde toda una vida de soledad..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3916
translate spanish d21b401_56eedb2a:

    # Z "Maybe this does not have to end here."
    Z "Quizá esto no tenga que terminar aquí."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3919
translate spanish d21b401_1bbf6ebf:

    # I "What... do you mean by that, [persistent.player_name]?"
    I "¿Qué... quieres decir con eso, [persistent.player_name]?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3925
translate spanish d21b401_ff326d58:

    # Z "Our chapter... and us."
    Z "Nuestro capítulo... y nosotros."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3926
translate spanish d21b401_493ade5a:

    # Z "You have fascinated me the moment I saw you."
    Z "Me fascinaste desde el momento en que te vi."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3929
translate spanish d21b401_16f1a9f6:

    # Z "...Everything about you, not just your mysteriously shifting eyes."
    Z "...Todo en ti, no solo tus ojos que cambian misteriosamente."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3932
translate spanish d21b401_fea67d72:

    # "She blushes..."
    "Se sonroja..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3935
translate spanish d21b401_471ae966:

    # "...and then, her smile returns. And her eyes; blue, like yours."
    "… y entonces, su sonrisa vuelve. Y sus ojos; azules, como los tuyos."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3938
translate spanish d21b401_fccb2222:

    # I "I... will remember your words, [persistent.player_name]."
    I "Yo... recordaré tus palabras, [persistent.player_name]."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3941
translate spanish d21b401_62c3dd77:

    # I "But we both know that to begin something new, we also must let go of the old."
    I "Pero ambos sabemos que para empezar algo nuevo, también debemos soltar lo viejo."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3945
translate spanish d21b401_09081c12:

    # "You look into her eyes, trying to understand the meaning of her words..."
    "Miras sus ojos, tratando de entender el significado de sus palabras..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3948
translate spanish d21b401_3c3c9369:

    # "...and hold her, as she leans back a little."
    "… y la abrazas, mientras ella se inclina un poco hacia atrás."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3951
translate spanish d21b401_09915540:

    # I "All we can do now, is to not let this night end just yet."
    I "Todo lo que podemos hacer ahora, es no dejar que esta noche termine todavía."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3954
translate spanish d21b401_9889195d:

    # "Smiling, she looks deeply into your eyes. Her words still echoing through your mind."
    "Sonriendo, te mira profundamente a los ojos. Sus palabras aún resuenan en tu mente."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3955
translate spanish d21b401_068dc21d:

    # "A mix of yearning... and loss seeps through you."
    "Una mezcla de anhelo... y pérdida se filtra en ti."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3956
translate spanish d21b401_d62de73e:

    # "A feeling that you are looking into the eyes of an impossibly old soul that is making an effort to be there with you, and yet, fading away as the night goes on."
    "La sensación de que estás mirando a los ojos de un alma increíblemente vieja que se esfuerza por estar ahí contigo, y sin embargo, se desvanece a medida que avanza la noche."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3957
translate spanish d21b401_bf3b87c1:

    # "The intoxication you felt at the taste of her lips on yours is something that moves beyond physical pleasure, the limits of sexual play."
    "La embriaguez que sentiste al saborear sus labios sobre los tuyos es algo que va más allá del placer físico, de los límites del juego sexual."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3958
translate spanish d21b401_387887ac:

    # "You recognise that whatever the future might bring, this night will stay with you for as long as you will live."
    "Reconoces que, sea lo que sea lo que depare el futuro, esta noche permanecerá contigo mientras vivas."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3961
translate spanish d21b401_ee7386b7:

    # "And as you kiss, that acceptance becomes easier, only to flee again once your lips will be separated."
    "Y mientras besas, esa aceptación se vuelve más fácil, solo para huir de nuevo una vez que vuestros labios se separen."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3962
translate spanish d21b401_3dc9929b:

    # "But to regret the future, is to miss out on the present. And so you kiss for a while longer, under the moonlight..."
    "Pero arrepentirse del futuro, es perderse el presente. Y así besáis un rato más, bajo la luz de la luna..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3966
translate spanish d21b401_0a627c53:

    # "...until the inevitable end of the night comes, and the dream slips away."
    "...hasta que llega el inevitable final de la noche, y el sueño se desvanece."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3971
translate spanish d21b401_f1a3cbfb:

    # Z "This night. It does not have to end yet."
    Z "Esta noche. No tiene que terminar todavía."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3974
translate spanish d21b401_c19ac202_1:

    # "She smiles..."
    "Sonríe..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3977
translate spanish d21b401_503a2431:

    # "You hold her tight, as she lowers herself onto you further..."
    "La abrazas fuerte, mientras ella se desliza más sobre ti..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3980
translate spanish d21b401_b0d82b93:

    # I "You are right, [persistent.player_name]."
    I "Tienes razón, [persistent.player_name]."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3981
translate spanish d21b401_f84b5e5c:

    # I "It does not have to end just yet."
    I "No tiene que terminar todavía."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3984
translate spanish d21b401_d7472930:

    # "She looks at you, with renewed eagerness..."
    "Te mira, con renovado entusiasmo..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3987
translate spanish d21b401_7cf6c5a2:

    # "...and kisses you, while her hips start to move again."
    "...y te besa, mientras sus caderas empiezan a moverse de nuevo."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3988
translate spanish d21b401_cfec6572:

    # "You enjoy the dream as long as it lasts. But all dreams eventually come to an end, and before you know it..."
    "Disfrutas del sueño mientras dure. Pero todos los sueños llegan a su fin, y antes de que te des cuenta..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:3992
translate spanish d21b401_1318b844:

    # "...you fall asleep, together, firmly wrapped in one another."
    "...os quedáis dormidos, juntos, firmemente envueltos el uno en el otro."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:4002
translate spanish d21b415_4cc5803e:

    # "The next morning..."
    "A la mañana siguiente..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:4006
translate spanish d21b415_ebc3c498:

    # I "[persistent.player_name]?"
    I "¿[persistent.player_name]?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:4009
translate spanish d21b415_4ec3ddfe:

    # Z "mh... yes?"
    Z "mh... ¿sí?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:4015
translate spanish d21b415_0f662244:

    # I "Sorry for waking you up. But I figured you have not eaten anything since yesterday, so..."
    I "Siento haberte despertado. Pero supuse que no habías comido nada desde ayer, así que..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:4017
translate spanish d21b415_885a5678:

    # I "Sorry for waking you up. But I figured you'd want to see the fruits of yesterday's labor."
    I "Siento haberte despertado. Pero supuse que querrías ver los frutos del trabajo de ayer."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:4020
translate spanish d21b415_abd6994a:

    # I "I... made you something to get the day started."
    I "Te... he preparado algo para empezar el día."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:4023
translate spanish d21b415_a40cd8b0:

    # I "It's maybe not like what you get in the city, but I think it turned out well!"
    I "Quizá no sea como lo que consigues en la ciudad, ¡pero creo que ha quedado bien!"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:4026
translate spanish d21b415_61d8c88f:

    # Z "You... made this just this morning?"
    Z "¿Tú... has hecho esto esta misma mañana?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:4027
translate spanish d21b415_306e8f64:

    # I "mhm..."
    I "mhm..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:4030
translate spanish d21b415_dba23b05:

    # Z "You didn't have to, but thank you. And you're right, now that you mention it..."
    Z "No tenías por qué, pero gracias. Y tienes razón, ahora que lo mencionas..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:4033
translate spanish d21b415_2738d106:

    # "...I am feeling quite hungry, indeed."
    "...la verdad es que tengo bastante hambre."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:4036
translate spanish d21b415_a51bb635:

    # I "I will put this down here. I also brought your clothes."
    I "Dejaré esto aquí. También te he traído tu ropa."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:4039
translate spanish d21b415_88506eb4:

    # Z "Sure, thank you..."
    Z "Claro, gracias..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:4041
translate spanish d21b415_bd225f81:

    # Zt "She's a gem..."
    Zt "Es una joya..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:4043
translate spanish d21b415_ec56d5b8:

    # Zt "She is truly adorable."
    Zt "Es realmente adorable."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:4045
translate spanish d21b415_055aae8f:

    # Zt "She's a sweet one."
    Zt "Es un amor."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:4048
translate spanish d21b415_bcef6b1b:

    # C "Yuna?"
    C "¿Yuna?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:4051
translate spanish d21b415_5018f220:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:4054
translate spanish d21b415_e5360a02:

    # C "Yuna... I..."
    C "Yuna... yo..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:4060
translate spanish d21b415_20d1ec4e:

    # So "...I'm back."
    So "...he vuelto."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:4065
translate spanish d21b415_936cffe1:

    # I "S-Sonmi...?!"
    I "¿S-Sonmi...?!"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:4068
translate spanish d21b415_c875db1a:

    # I "Sonmi... are you hurt?"
    I "Sonmi... ¿estás herida?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:4071
translate spanish d21b415_98782931:

    # I "H-how are you? Tell me..."
    I "¿C-cómo estás? Dime..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:4073
translate spanish d21b415_b5e3f821:

    # So "I..."
    So "Yo..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:4078
translate spanish d21b415_f20b023f:

    # So "...I feel better."
    So "...me siento mejor."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:4079
translate spanish d21b415_d22fc610:

    # I "{i}*gasp*{/i}"
    I "{i}*jadeo*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:4082
translate spanish d21b415_2b5dcbcd:

    # I "Your..."
    I "Tus..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:4085
translate spanish d21b415_b1a25a6e:

    # I "...your eyes."
    I "...tus ojos."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:4092
translate spanish d21b415_360ae2d8:

    # So "...!"
    So "...!"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:4093
translate spanish d21b415_652ef79e:

    # I "You're really back!"
    I "¡Has vuelto de verdad!"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:4096
translate spanish d21b415_c4dcb006:

    # So "I'm sorry, Yuna. For everything..."
    So "Lo siento, Yuna. Por todo..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:4099
translate spanish d21b415_e77a92bf:

    # So "...all these years!"
    So "...¡todos estos años!"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:4102
translate spanish d21b415_07255685:

    # I "It's fine..."
    I "Está bien..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:4103
translate spanish d21b415_33ebdfcf:

    # I "You don't need to go out there anymore."
    I "Ya no necesitas salir ahí fuera."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:4106
translate spanish d21b415_6ec9609c:

    # So "{i}*cries*{/i} I don't want to. I really want to move on..."
    So "{i}*llora*{/i} No quiero. De verdad quiero seguir adelante..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:4109
translate spanish d21b415_d9ffcdb6:

    # I "And we will, together."
    I "Y lo haremos, juntas."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:4110
translate spanish d21b415_67711ea4:

    # So "Yes, please..."
    So "Sí, por favor..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:4113
translate spanish d21b415_2e1f09ae:

    # "You slowly approach the two women..."
    "Te acercas lentamente a las dos mujeres..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:4116
translate spanish d21b415_6c2df7e5:

    # So "{i}*sobs*{/i}"
    So "{i}*sollozos*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:4119
translate spanish d21b415_e71ea6e6:

    # "...and notice her looking at you."
    "...y notas que ella te mira."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:4122
translate spanish d21b415_0aefb446:

    # So "Yuna, give me one moment, please."
    So "Yuna, dame un momento, por favor."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:4125
translate spanish d21b415_b9617404:

    # "She stands before you..."
    "Se pone frente a ti..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:4128
translate spanish d21b415_0fc5feee:

    # "Hesitating to look at you, she tries to form her words."
    "Dudando en mirarte, intenta formar sus palabras."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:4131
translate spanish d21b415_c9c6d2c8:

    # So "Thank you for your help, [persistent.player_name]."
    So "Gracias por tu ayuda, [persistent.player_name]."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:4134
translate spanish d21b415_b581cf5c:

    # Z "Don't mention it, Sonmi."
    Z "No hay de qué, Sonmi."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:4142
translate spanish d21b415_a5d746bf:

    # Z "...!"
    Z "...!"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:4143
translate spanish d21b415_c106c5c6:

    # "She hugs you tight..."
    "Te abraza fuerte..."

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:4146
translate spanish d21b415_f262092e:

    # Z "Are you... by any chance hungry?"
    Z "¿Tienes... hambre, por casualidad?"

# game/scripts/day21.rpy:4147
translate spanish d21b415_049923f6:

    # So "Yes..."
    So "Sí..."

