    # game/scripts/day21.rpy:1771
    old "It was a difficult day for Sonmi, and despite her best efforts, [I] could not prevent her from leaving the hideout again. Still, one long-held wish finally came true; I was able to show her the old message from before the incident. If there is a light spot to be taken from this day, it is that [I] and I have grown considerably closer. She is a fascinating, wise, and strikingly attractive woman from another era, and I am seeing myself increasingly drawn to her."
    new "Fue un día difícil para Sonmi, y a pesar de sus mejores esfuerzos, [I] no pudo evitar que volviera a abandonar el escondite. Aun así, un deseo largamente acariciado finalmente se cumplió; pude mostrarle el viejo mensaje de antes del incidente. Si hay un punto positivo que sacar de este día, es que [I] y yo nos hemos acercado considerablemente. Es una mujer fascinante, sabia y sorprendentemente atractiva de otra época, y me veo cada vez más atraído por ella."

